1
00:01:48,283 --> 00:01:50,702
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Bloody kids.</font></b>

2
00:02:37,165 --> 00:02:40,836
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">How fastidious you've become,
Wormtail.</font></b>

3
00:02:41,002 --> 00:02:45,382
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">As I recall, you once called
the nearest gutter pipe home.</font></b>

4
00:02:45,549 --> 00:02:50,762
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Could it be that the task of nursing me
has become wearysome for you?</font></b>

5
00:02:50,929 --> 00:02:53,390
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Oh, no. No, no, my Lord Voldemort.</font></b>

6
00:02:53,598 --> 00:02:54,850
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I only meant...</font></b>

7
00:02:55,016 --> 00:02:57,978
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...perhaps if we were to do it
without the boy.</font></b>

8
00:02:58,145 --> 00:03:00,522
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No! The boy is everything!</font></b>

9
00:03:00,689 --> 00:03:04,234
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It cannot be done without him.
And it will be done.</font></b>

10
00:03:04,401 --> 00:03:07,070
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Exactly as I said.</font></b>

11
00:03:07,529 --> 00:03:11,199
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- I will not disappoint you, my Lord.
- Good.</font></b>

12
00:03:11,366 --> 00:03:14,411
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">First, gather our old comrades.</font></b>

13
00:03:14,578 --> 00:03:16,830
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Send them a sign.</font></b>

14
00:03:28,550 --> 00:03:32,053
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Nagini tells me
the old Muggle caretaker...</font></b>

15
00:03:32,220 --> 00:03:35,891
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...is standing just outside the door.</font></b>

16
00:03:36,057 --> 00:03:41,396
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Step aside, Wormtail,
so I can give our guest a proper greeting.</font></b>

17
00:03:41,563 --> 00:03:43,398
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Avada Kedavra!</i></font></b>

18
00:03:48,403 --> 00:03:49,905
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Harry.</font></b>

19
00:03:50,655 --> 00:03:52,324
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Harry!</font></b>

20
00:03:53,617 --> 00:03:55,410
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Are you all right?</font></b>

21
00:03:56,119 --> 00:03:58,246
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Hermione. Bad dream.</font></b>

22
00:03:58,413 --> 00:04:01,750
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- When did you get here?
- Just now. You?</font></b>

23
00:04:01,917 --> 00:04:03,168
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Last night.</font></b>

24
00:04:03,335 --> 00:04:05,587
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Wake up! Wake up, Ronald!</font></b>

25
00:04:05,754 --> 00:04:07,005
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Bloody hell.</font></b>

26
00:04:07,172 --> 00:04:08,673
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Honestly, get dressed.</font></b>

27
00:04:09,424 --> 00:04:11,176
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">And don't go back to sleep.</font></b>

28
00:04:11,343 --> 00:04:14,679
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Come on, Ron!
Your mother says breakfast's ready!</font></b>

29
00:04:21,353 --> 00:04:24,189
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Ron, where are we actually going?
- Don't know.</font></b>

30
00:04:24,648 --> 00:04:27,943
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Hey, Dad. Where are we going?
- Haven't the foggiest.</font></b>

31
00:04:28,109 --> 00:04:29,611
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Keep up!</font></b>

32
00:04:32,197 --> 00:04:34,032
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Arthur!</font></b>

33
00:04:34,199 --> 00:04:36,201
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It's about time, son.</font></b>

34
00:04:36,368 --> 00:04:40,747
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Sorry, Amos. Some of us
had a bit of a sleepy start.</font></b>

35
00:04:40,914 --> 00:04:46,586
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">This is Amos Diggory, everyone.
Works with me at the Ministry.</font></b>

36
00:04:46,795 --> 00:04:49,297
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">And this strapping young lad
must be Cedric, am I right?</font></b>

37
00:04:49,464 --> 00:04:50,632
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Yes, sir.</font></b>

38
00:04:50,799 --> 00:04:52,467
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">This way.</font></b>

39
00:04:54,177 --> 00:04:57,556
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Merlin's beard!
You must be Harry Potter.</font></b>

40
00:04:57,722 --> 00:05:00,475
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Yes, sir.
- Great, great pleasure.</font></b>

41
00:05:00,642 --> 00:05:02,435
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Pleasure to meet you too, sir.</font></b>

42
00:05:05,063 --> 00:05:07,732
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Yes, it's just over there.</font></b>

43
00:05:09,985 --> 00:05:11,820
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Shall we?
- Oh, yeah.</font></b>

44
00:05:11,987 --> 00:05:13,155
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">We don't want to be late.</font></b>

45
00:05:13,321 --> 00:05:17,492
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Come on. Nearly there now.
Get yourself into a good position.</font></b>

46
00:05:18,493 --> 00:05:20,829
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Why are they all standing around
that manky old boot?</font></b>

47
00:05:20,996 --> 00:05:23,498
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- That isn't just any manky old boot.
- It's a Portkey.</font></b>

48
00:05:23,665 --> 00:05:25,000
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Time to go!</font></b>

49
00:05:25,167 --> 00:05:26,793
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What's a Portkey?</font></b>

50
00:05:26,960 --> 00:05:31,006
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Ready! After 3. 1, 2...
- Harry!</font></b>

51
00:05:31,173 --> 00:05:32,257
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...3!</font></b>

52
00:05:43,310 --> 00:05:44,436
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Let go, kids!</font></b>

53
00:05:44,603 --> 00:05:47,189
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- What?!
- Let go!</font></b>

54
00:05:59,242 --> 00:06:01,828
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I'll bet that cleared your sinuses, eh?</font></b>

55
00:06:02,871 --> 00:06:05,373
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Total shambles, as per usual.
- Thanks.</font></b>

56
00:06:11,171 --> 00:06:13,298
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Go on, look at that!</font></b>

57
00:06:13,548 --> 00:06:18,053
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Well, kids, welcome to
the Quidditch World Cup!</font></b>

58
00:06:21,056 --> 00:06:23,725
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Stay together! Keep up, girls!</font></b>

59
00:06:25,227 --> 00:06:26,520
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Look!</font></b>

60
00:06:27,395 --> 00:06:29,689
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Come on! Keep up, girls!</font></b>

61
00:06:36,571 --> 00:06:37,989
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Blimey!</font></b>

62
00:06:38,156 --> 00:06:40,033
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Parting of the ways, I think, old chap.</font></b>

63
00:06:40,200 --> 00:06:41,576
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- See you at the match.
- See you.</font></b>

64
00:06:41,743 --> 00:06:43,078
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Cedric.
- Ced, come on.</font></b>

65
00:06:43,245 --> 00:06:44,913
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">See you later, Cedric.</font></b>

66
00:06:49,543 --> 00:06:51,628
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Home sweet home.</font></b>

67
00:06:53,421 --> 00:06:54,965
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What?</font></b>

68
00:07:02,389 --> 00:07:04,266
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Excellent, excellent.
- Ginny, look!</font></b>

69
00:07:04,432 --> 00:07:05,767
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- All to the bath.
- Look.</font></b>

70
00:07:05,934 --> 00:07:08,436
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Girls, choose a bunk and unpack.</font></b>

71
00:07:09,020 --> 00:07:11,439
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Ron, get out of the kitchen.
We're all hungry.</font></b>

72
00:07:11,606 --> 00:07:14,109
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Yeah, get out of the kitchen, Ron!
- Feet off the table!</font></b>

73
00:07:14,276 --> 00:07:16,570
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Feet off the table!
- Feet off the table!</font></b>

74
00:07:17,779 --> 00:07:19,948
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I love magic.</font></b>

75
00:07:35,297 --> 00:07:38,675
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Get your Quidditch World Cup
programs here!</font></b>

76
00:07:38,967 --> 00:07:42,137
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Blimey, Dad. How far up are we?</font></b>

77
00:07:42,304 --> 00:07:43,722
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Well, put it this way:</font></b>

78
00:07:43,972 --> 00:07:45,682
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">If it rains...</font></b>

79
00:07:45,849 --> 00:07:48,185
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...you'll be the first to know.</font></b>

80
00:07:48,977 --> 00:07:51,354
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Father and I are in
the minister's box...</font></b>

81
00:07:51,521 --> 00:07:54,816
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...by personal invitation
of Cornelius Fudge himself.</font></b>

82
00:07:54,983 --> 00:07:57,152
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Don't boast, Draco.</font></b>

83
00:07:57,319 --> 00:07:59,446
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">There's no need with these people.</font></b>

84
00:08:01,907 --> 00:08:04,409
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Do enjoy yourself, won't you?</font></b>

85
00:08:04,826 --> 00:08:06,661
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">While you can.</font></b>

86
00:08:20,050 --> 00:08:24,721
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Come on up. Take your seats. I told you
these seats would be worth waiting for.</font></b>

87
00:08:24,888 --> 00:08:26,765
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Come on!</font></b>

88
00:08:29,017 --> 00:08:30,977
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It's the Irish! There's Troy!</font></b>

89
00:08:31,144 --> 00:08:32,979
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- And Mullet!
- And Moran!</font></b>

90
00:08:38,652 --> 00:08:41,530
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Ireland! Ireland! Ireland!</i></font></b>

91
00:08:45,784 --> 00:08:48,995
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Here come the Bulgarians!
- Yes!</font></b>

92
00:08:55,043 --> 00:08:56,419
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Who's that?</font></b>

93
00:08:57,212 --> 00:09:00,215
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">That, sis, is the best Seeker
in the world.</font></b>

94
00:09:02,259 --> 00:09:05,804
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Krum! Krum! Krum!</i></font></b>

95
00:09:10,559 --> 00:09:11,768
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Krum!</font></b>

96
00:09:11,935 --> 00:09:13,687
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Yes!</font></b>

97
00:09:21,403 --> 00:09:23,321
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Good evening!</font></b>

98
00:09:23,864 --> 00:09:26,867
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">As Minister for Magic...</font></b>

99
00:09:27,075 --> 00:09:30,120
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...it gives me great pleasure...</font></b>

100
00:09:30,745 --> 00:09:34,499
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...to welcome
each and every one of you...</font></b>

101
00:09:34,666 --> 00:09:40,547
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...to the final
of the 422nd Quidditch World Cup!</font></b>

102
00:09:41,173 --> 00:09:42,549
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Let the match...</font></b>

103
00:09:42,924 --> 00:09:44,509
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...begin!</font></b>

104
00:09:50,640 --> 00:09:52,809
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Krum! Krum! Krum!</i></font></b>

105
00:10:00,650 --> 00:10:02,319
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">There's no one like Krum.</font></b>

106
00:10:02,486 --> 00:10:04,112
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Krum?
- Dumb Krum?</font></b>

107
00:10:04,279 --> 00:10:07,324
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">He's like a bird,
the way he rides the wind.</font></b>

108
00:10:07,491 --> 00:10:10,410
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- He's more than an athlete.
- Dumb Krum.</font></b>

109
00:10:10,577 --> 00:10:11,953
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">He's an artist.</font></b>

110
00:10:12,120 --> 00:10:14,289
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- I think you're in love, Ron.
- Shut up.</font></b>

111
00:10:14,498 --> 00:10:15,957
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Viktor, I love you</i></font></b>

112
00:10:16,124 --> 00:10:17,751
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Viktor, I do</i></font></b>

113
00:10:17,918 --> 00:10:21,129
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>When we're apart
My heart beats only for you</i></font></b>

114
00:10:21,296 --> 00:10:23,965
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Sounds like the Irish
have got their pride on.</font></b>

115
00:10:24,132 --> 00:10:25,884
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Stop! Stop it!</font></b>

116
00:10:26,426 --> 00:10:28,011
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It's not the Irish.</font></b>

117
00:10:29,137 --> 00:10:31,306
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">We've gotta get out of here. Now!</font></b>

118
00:10:33,433 --> 00:10:35,811
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Get out, it's the Death Eaters!</font></b>

119
00:10:35,977 --> 00:10:39,314
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Get back to the Portkey, everybody,
and stick together!</font></b>

120
00:10:39,481 --> 00:10:42,150
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Fred, George!
Ginny is your responsibility.</font></b>

121
00:10:42,692 --> 00:10:44,486
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Go!</font></b>

122
00:10:44,653 --> 00:10:46,488
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Harry!</font></b>

123
00:11:01,294 --> 00:11:03,463
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Keep up, you lot!
- Harry!</font></b>

124
00:11:04,714 --> 00:11:06,842
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Harry! Harry!</font></b>

125
00:11:54,514 --> 00:11:56,016
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Morsmordre!</i></font></b>

126
00:12:22,751 --> 00:12:24,252
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Harry!</font></b>

127
00:12:25,754 --> 00:12:28,965
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Where are you?
- Harry!</font></b>

128
00:12:30,217 --> 00:12:32,844
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">We've been looking for you for ages!</font></b>

129
00:12:33,929 --> 00:12:35,764
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Thought we lost you, mate.</font></b>

130
00:12:36,598 --> 00:12:38,600
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What is that?</font></b>

131
00:12:41,686 --> 00:12:43,772
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Stupefy!</i></font></b>

132
00:12:43,939 --> 00:12:45,273
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Stop!</font></b>

133
00:12:45,440 --> 00:12:47,651
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">That's my son!</font></b>

134
00:12:48,693 --> 00:12:51,363
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Ron, Harry, Hermione, you all right?
- We came back for Harry.</font></b>

135
00:12:51,530 --> 00:12:52,823
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Which of you conjured it?</font></b>

136
00:12:52,989 --> 00:12:55,200
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Crouch, you can't possi...
- Do not lie!</font></b>

137
00:12:55,367 --> 00:12:57,327
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You've been discovered
at the scene of the crime.</font></b>

138
00:12:57,494 --> 00:12:59,538
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Crime?
- Barty! They're just kids.</font></b>

139
00:12:59,704 --> 00:13:01,206
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What crime?</font></b>

140
00:13:01,373 --> 00:13:03,875
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It's the Dark Mark, Harry.
It's his mark.</font></b>

141
00:13:04,042 --> 00:13:05,210
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What, Voldemort?</font></b>

142
00:13:06,378 --> 00:13:10,257
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Those people tonight, in the masks,
they're his too, aren't they?</font></b>

143
00:13:10,423 --> 00:13:12,634
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- His followers?
- Yeah.</font></b>

144
00:13:12,843 --> 00:13:14,719
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Death Eaters.</font></b>

145
00:13:15,470 --> 00:13:19,474
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Follow me.
- There was a man, before.</font></b>

146
00:13:19,975 --> 00:13:21,309
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">There!</font></b>

147
00:13:21,476 --> 00:13:23,812
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">All of you, this way!</font></b>

148
00:13:24,521 --> 00:13:25,981
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">A man, Harry?</font></b>

149
00:13:26,273 --> 00:13:27,732
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Who?</font></b>

150
00:13:28,150 --> 00:13:29,943
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I don't know.</font></b>

151
00:13:31,570 --> 00:13:33,780
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I didn't see his face.</font></b>

152
00:13:50,005 --> 00:13:53,133
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Anything from the trolley?</font></b>

153
00:13:54,134 --> 00:13:57,262
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Anything from the trolley?</font></b>

154
00:14:01,183 --> 00:14:02,934
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Anything from the trolley, dears?</font></b>

155
00:14:03,101 --> 00:14:05,312
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Packet of Drooble's...</font></b>

156
00:14:05,479 --> 00:14:07,272
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...and a Licorice Wand.</font></b>

157
00:14:08,732 --> 00:14:10,817
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">On second thought, just the Drooble's.</font></b>

158
00:14:10,984 --> 00:14:14,988
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- It's all right, I'll get it. Don't worry.
- Just the Drooble's. Thanks.</font></b>

159
00:14:16,239 --> 00:14:18,658
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Two Pumpkin Pasties, please.</font></b>

160
00:14:24,039 --> 00:14:25,665
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Thank you.</font></b>

161
00:14:26,291 --> 00:14:28,502
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Anything sweet for you, dear?</font></b>

162
00:14:29,336 --> 00:14:31,671
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Oh, no, I'm not hungry. Thank you.</font></b>

163
00:14:32,589 --> 00:14:34,591
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Anything from the trolley?</font></b>

164
00:14:34,758 --> 00:14:36,802
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">This is horrible.</font></b>

165
00:14:37,177 --> 00:14:39,888
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">How can the Ministry
not know who conjured it?</font></b>

166
00:14:40,096 --> 00:14:41,848
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Wasn't there any security or...?</font></b>

167
00:14:42,015 --> 00:14:44,810
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Loads, according to Dad.</font></b>

168
00:14:44,976 --> 00:14:48,939
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">That's what worried them so much.
Happened right under their noses.</font></b>

169
00:14:51,566 --> 00:14:54,986
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It's hurting again, isn't it?
Your scar.</font></b>

170
00:14:55,153 --> 00:14:56,822
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I'm fine.</font></b>

171
00:14:58,865 --> 00:15:01,743
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You know Sirius will
want to hear about this...</font></b>

172
00:15:01,910 --> 00:15:05,914
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...what you saw at the World Cup
and the dream.</font></b>

173
00:15:14,339 --> 00:15:17,551
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Hedwig. There we go.</font></b>

174
00:15:56,715 --> 00:15:59,009
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Clear the runway!</font></b>

175
00:16:04,431 --> 00:16:07,184
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Well, there's something
you don't see every day.</font></b>

176
00:16:31,166 --> 00:16:36,087
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Well, now we're all settled in and sorted,
I'd like to make an announcement.</i></font></b>

177
00:16:37,088 --> 00:16:40,509
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">This castle will not only be
your home this year...</font></b>

178
00:16:40,675 --> 00:16:43,845
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...but home to some
very special guests as well.</font></b>

179
00:16:44,179 --> 00:16:46,765
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You see, Hogwarts has been chosen...</font></b>

180
00:16:47,766 --> 00:16:49,267
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Yes, what is it?</font></b>

181
00:16:49,476 --> 00:16:50,852
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What is it?</font></b>

182
00:16:53,188 --> 00:16:56,525
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Tell them to wait.
Tell them to wait. Wait.</font></b>

183
00:16:56,691 --> 00:17:02,656
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">So Hogwarts has been chosen
to host a legendary event:</font></b>

184
00:17:02,823 --> 00:17:04,866
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The Triwizard Tournament.</font></b>

185
00:17:05,408 --> 00:17:07,494
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- For those of you who do not know...
- Brilliant.</font></b>

186
00:17:07,661 --> 00:17:10,831
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...the Triwizard Tournament
brings together three schools...</font></b>

187
00:17:10,997 --> 00:17:13,124
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...for a series of magical contests.</font></b>

188
00:17:13,291 --> 00:17:16,753
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">From each school, a single student
is selected to compete.</font></b>

189
00:17:17,003 --> 00:17:18,713
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Now let me be clear.</font></b>

190
00:17:18,880 --> 00:17:21,800
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">If chosen, you stand alone.</font></b>

191
00:17:21,967 --> 00:17:23,885
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">And trust me when I say...</font></b>

192
00:17:24,052 --> 00:17:27,055
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...these contests are not
for the faint-hearted.</font></b>

193
00:17:27,347 --> 00:17:31,685
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">But more of that later.
For now, please join me in welcoming...</font></b>

194
00:17:31,852 --> 00:17:35,897
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...the lovely ladies of the
Beauxbatons Academy of Magic...</font></b>

195
00:17:36,064 --> 00:17:40,026
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...and their headmistress,
Madame Maxime.</font></b>

196
00:17:52,581 --> 00:17:54,124
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Bloody hell.</font></b>

197
00:18:02,007 --> 00:18:04,342
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Blimey. That's one big woman.</font></b>

198
00:18:26,364 --> 00:18:28,450
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">And now our friends from the north.</font></b>

199
00:18:28,617 --> 00:18:31,453
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Please greet the proud sons
of Durmstrang...</font></b>

200
00:18:31,620 --> 00:18:34,414
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...and their high master,
Igor Karkaroff.</font></b>

201
00:18:57,479 --> 00:18:59,064
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Oh, it's Krum!</font></b>

202
00:18:59,231 --> 00:19:00,690
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Blimey, it's him!</font></b>

203
00:19:00,857 --> 00:19:02,734
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Viktor Krum!</font></b>

204
00:19:11,660 --> 00:19:13,078
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Albus.</font></b>

205
00:19:13,245 --> 00:19:14,955
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Igor.</font></b>

206
00:19:28,593 --> 00:19:32,264
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Professor Dumbly-dorr,
my horses have traveled a long way.</font></b>

207
00:19:32,430 --> 00:19:34,975
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- They will need attending to.
- Don't worry, Madame Maxime.</font></b>

208
00:19:35,142 --> 00:19:38,687
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Our gamekeeper, Hagrid,
is more than capable of seeing to them.</font></b>

209
00:19:38,854 --> 00:19:41,106
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">But you know, Monsieur Hagrid...</font></b>

210
00:19:41,606 --> 00:19:43,900
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...they drink only single-malt whiskey.</font></b>

211
00:19:50,198 --> 00:19:51,867
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You idiot!</font></b>

212
00:19:56,872 --> 00:19:58,874
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Your attention, please!</font></b>

213
00:20:01,251 --> 00:20:03,378
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I'd like to say a few words.</font></b>

214
00:20:05,130 --> 00:20:07,174
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Eternal glory.</font></b>

215
00:20:07,632 --> 00:20:11,678
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">That is what awaits the student
who wins the Triwizard Tournament.</font></b>

216
00:20:11,845 --> 00:20:16,057
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">But to do this, that student
must survive three tasks.</font></b>

217
00:20:16,224 --> 00:20:20,103
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Three extremely dangerous tasks.</font></b>

218
00:20:20,604 --> 00:20:21,688
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Wicked.
- Wicked.</font></b>

219
00:20:21,855 --> 00:20:26,026
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">For this reason, the Ministry has seen fit
to impose a new rule.</font></b>

220
00:20:26,193 --> 00:20:27,569
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">To explain all this...</font></b>

221
00:20:27,736 --> 00:20:31,364
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...we have the head of the Department
of International Magical Cooperation...</font></b>

222
00:20:31,531 --> 00:20:33,658
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...Mr. Bartemius Crouch.</font></b>

223
00:20:48,089 --> 00:20:50,801
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Bloody hell. It's Mad-Eye Moody.</font></b>

224
00:20:51,593 --> 00:20:54,805
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Alastor Moody? The Auror?
- Auror?</font></b>

225
00:20:54,971 --> 00:20:58,433
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Dark-wizard catcher. Half the cells
in Azkaban are filled thanks to him.</font></b>

226
00:20:59,142 --> 00:21:02,270
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">He's supposed to be mad as a hatter,
though, these days.</font></b>

227
00:21:14,032 --> 00:21:17,786
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- My dear old friend, thanks for coming.
- Stupid ceiling.</font></b>

228
00:21:17,953 --> 00:21:19,079
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Thank you.</font></b>

229
00:21:25,585 --> 00:21:27,462
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What's that he's drinking,
do you suppose?</font></b>

230
00:21:27,879 --> 00:21:30,882
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I don't know, but I don't think
it's pumpkin juice.</font></b>

231
00:21:37,848 --> 00:21:39,808
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">After due consideration...</font></b>

232
00:21:39,975 --> 00:21:42,853
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...the Ministry has concluded that,
for their own safety...</font></b>

233
00:21:43,019 --> 00:21:45,981
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...no student under the age of 17...</font></b>

234
00:21:46,148 --> 00:21:49,901
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...shall be allowed to put forth their
name for the Triwizard Tournament.</font></b>

235
00:21:50,068 --> 00:21:52,779
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- This decision is final.
- That's rubbish!</font></b>

236
00:21:52,946 --> 00:21:55,532
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">That's rubbish!
You don't know what you're doing!</font></b>

237
00:21:55,699 --> 00:21:59,452
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Silence!
- They're not too happy about that, then.</font></b>

238
00:22:18,847 --> 00:22:21,266
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The Goblet of Fire.</font></b>

239
00:22:21,850 --> 00:22:24,728
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Anyone wishing to submit themselves
to the tournament...</font></b>

240
00:22:24,895 --> 00:22:27,814
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...need only write their name
upon a piece of parchment...</font></b>

241
00:22:27,981 --> 00:22:31,067
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...and throw it in the flame before
this hour on Thursday night.</font></b>

242
00:22:32,194 --> 00:22:34,404
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Do not do so lightly.</font></b>

243
00:22:34,779 --> 00:22:38,366
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">If chosen, there's no turning back.</font></b>

244
00:22:38,533 --> 00:22:43,497
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">As from this moment,
the Triwizard Tournament has begun.</font></b>

245
00:23:09,648 --> 00:23:11,733
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Alastor Moody.</font></b>

246
00:23:13,652 --> 00:23:15,278
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Ex-Auror...</font></b>

247
00:23:16,988 --> 00:23:19,407
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...Ministry malcontent...</font></b>

248
00:23:19,616 --> 00:23:22,035
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...and your new
Defense Against the Dark Arts teacher.</font></b>

249
00:23:22,202 --> 00:23:26,665
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I am here because Dumbledore asked me.
End of story, goodbye, the end.</font></b>

250
00:23:26,832 --> 00:23:28,583
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Any questions?</font></b>

251
00:23:31,753 --> 00:23:33,505
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">When it comes to the Dark Arts...</font></b>

252
00:23:34,881 --> 00:23:37,551
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...I believe in a practical approach.</font></b>

253
00:23:37,717 --> 00:23:43,431
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">But first, which of you can tell me
how many Unforgivable Curses there are?</font></b>

254
00:23:43,932 --> 00:23:46,268
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Three, sir.
- And they are so named?</font></b>

255
00:23:46,434 --> 00:23:49,688
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Because they are unforgivable.
The use of any one of them will...</font></b>

256
00:23:49,855 --> 00:23:53,942
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Will earn you a one-way ticket
to Azkaban, correct.</font></b>

257
00:23:54,151 --> 00:23:56,903
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The Ministry says you're too young
to see what these curses do.</font></b>

258
00:23:57,070 --> 00:24:00,532
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I say different! You need to know
what you're up against!</font></b>

259
00:24:00,699 --> 00:24:02,868
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You need to be prepared.</font></b>

260
00:24:03,034 --> 00:24:05,495
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You need to find another place
to put your chewing gum...</font></b>

261
00:24:05,662 --> 00:24:07,956
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...besides the underside of your desk,
Mr. Finnigan!</font></b>

262
00:24:08,123 --> 00:24:11,126
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No way. The old codger
can see out the back of his head.</font></b>

263
00:24:11,835 --> 00:24:13,587
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">And hear across classrooms!</font></b>

264
00:24:15,964 --> 00:24:19,468
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">So which curse shall we see first?</font></b>

265
00:24:19,634 --> 00:24:20,844
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Weasley!
- Yes?</font></b>

266
00:24:21,011 --> 00:24:22,345
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Stand.</font></b>

267
00:24:25,515 --> 00:24:27,309
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Give us a curse.</font></b>

268
00:24:27,476 --> 00:24:31,313
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Well, my dad did tell me about one.</font></b>

269
00:24:31,897 --> 00:24:33,148
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The Imperius Curse.</font></b>

270
00:24:33,315 --> 00:24:36,568
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Oh, yeah, your father
would know all about that.</font></b>

271
00:24:37,027 --> 00:24:39,696
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Gave the Ministry quite a bit of grief
a few years ago.</font></b>

272
00:24:40,155 --> 00:24:42,657
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Perhaps this will show you why.</font></b>

273
00:24:50,290 --> 00:24:51,625
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Hello.</font></b>

274
00:24:53,251 --> 00:24:54,961
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Lovely little beauty.</font></b>

275
00:24:58,089 --> 00:25:00,091
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Engorgio.</i></font></b>

276
00:25:00,467 --> 00:25:02,135
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Imperio!</i></font></b>

277
00:25:06,515 --> 00:25:08,975
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Don't worry. It's completely harmless.</font></b>

278
00:25:15,148 --> 00:25:16,817
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">If she bites...</font></b>

279
00:25:17,359 --> 00:25:18,860
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...she's lethal.</font></b>

280
00:25:21,363 --> 00:25:23,198
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What are you laughing at?</font></b>

281
00:25:24,533 --> 00:25:25,951
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Get off!</font></b>

282
00:25:28,370 --> 00:25:30,163
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Talented, isn't she?</font></b>

283
00:25:30,330 --> 00:25:33,708
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What should I have her do next?
Jump out the window?</font></b>

284
00:25:35,710 --> 00:25:37,087
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Drown herself?</font></b>

285
00:25:48,890 --> 00:25:52,144
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Scores of witches and wizards
have claimed...</font></b>

286
00:25:52,310 --> 00:25:56,314
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...that they only did
You-Know-Who's bidding...</font></b>

287
00:25:56,481 --> 00:25:58,733
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...under the influence
of the Imperius Curse.</font></b>

288
00:25:58,900 --> 00:26:00,819
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">But here's the rub:</font></b>

289
00:26:01,153 --> 00:26:04,156
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">How do we sort out the liars?</font></b>

290
00:26:06,491 --> 00:26:08,201
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Another, another.</font></b>

291
00:26:09,202 --> 00:26:10,745
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Up, up. Come on.</font></b>

292
00:26:10,912 --> 00:26:12,455
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Longbottom, is it?</font></b>

293
00:26:13,123 --> 00:26:14,624
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Up.</font></b>

294
00:26:16,668 --> 00:26:20,464
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Professor Sprout tells me
you have an aptitude for herbology.</font></b>

295
00:26:22,424 --> 00:26:24,092
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">There's the...</font></b>

296
00:26:24,301 --> 00:26:26,261
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The Cruciatus Curse.</font></b>

297
00:26:26,428 --> 00:26:29,264
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Correct, correct. Come, come.</font></b>

298
00:26:29,473 --> 00:26:31,099
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Particularly nasty.</font></b>

299
00:26:34,144 --> 00:26:35,979
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The torture curse.</font></b>

300
00:26:36,980 --> 00:26:39,149
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Crucio!</i></font></b>

301
00:26:51,870 --> 00:26:55,665
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Stop it! Can't you see
it's bothering him? Stop it!</font></b>

302
00:27:13,308 --> 00:27:17,312
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Perhaps you could give us the last
Unforgivable Curse, Miss Granger.</font></b>

303
00:27:19,731 --> 00:27:21,066
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No?</font></b>

304
00:27:22,275 --> 00:27:24,402
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Avada Kedavra!</i></font></b>

305
00:27:28,156 --> 00:27:29,699
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The Killing Curse.</font></b>

306
00:27:30,826 --> 00:27:33,995
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Only one person is known
to have survived it...</font></b>

307
00:27:34,538 --> 00:27:36,915
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...and he's sitting in this room.</font></b>

308
00:28:08,530 --> 00:28:10,282
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Brilliant, isn't he?</font></b>

309
00:28:10,448 --> 00:28:14,494
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Completely demented, of course, and
terrifying to be in the same room with...</font></b>

310
00:28:14,661 --> 00:28:17,831
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...but he's really been there, you know?
He's looked evil in the eye.</font></b>

311
00:28:17,998 --> 00:28:20,584
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">There's a reason those curses
are unforgivable.</font></b>

312
00:28:20,750 --> 00:28:24,921
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">To perform them in a classroom...
I mean, did you see Neville's face?</font></b>

313
00:28:27,799 --> 00:28:29,259
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Neville?</font></b>

314
00:28:29,426 --> 00:28:30,886
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Son?</font></b>

315
00:28:31,219 --> 00:28:32,888
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You all right?</font></b>

316
00:28:33,847 --> 00:28:37,225
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Come on. We'll have a cup of tea.
I want to show you something.</font></b>

317
00:28:51,740 --> 00:28:53,742
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">We're gonna be late!</font></b>

318
00:29:07,339 --> 00:29:09,674
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Come on, Cedric. Put it in!</font></b>

319
00:29:25,273 --> 00:29:27,776
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Eternal glory. Be brilliant, wouldn't it?</font></b>

320
00:29:27,943 --> 00:29:30,612
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Three years from now,
when we're old enough to be chosen.</font></b>

321
00:29:30,779 --> 00:29:32,405
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Yeah, rather you than me.</font></b>

322
00:29:32,572 --> 00:29:34,491
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Yes!</font></b>

323
00:29:36,701 --> 00:29:38,620
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Thank you, thank you.</font></b>

324
00:29:38,787 --> 00:29:41,832
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Well, lads, we've done it.
- Cooked it up just this morning.</font></b>

325
00:29:41,998 --> 00:29:44,167
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It's not going to work.</font></b>

326
00:29:45,377 --> 00:29:47,879
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Oh, yeah?
- And why is that, Granger?</font></b>

327
00:29:48,046 --> 00:29:51,007
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You see this? This is an Age Line.</font></b>

328
00:29:51,174 --> 00:29:52,968
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Dumbledore drew it himself.</font></b>

329
00:29:53,135 --> 00:29:54,594
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">So?</font></b>

330
00:29:56,179 --> 00:29:59,808
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">So a genius like Dumbledore
couldn't possibly be fooled...</font></b>

331
00:29:59,975 --> 00:30:02,978
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...by a dodge as pathetically dimwitted
as an Aging Potion.</font></b>

332
00:30:03,145 --> 00:30:07,399
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- But that's why it's so brilliant.
- Because it's so pathetically dimwitted.</font></b>

333
00:30:09,151 --> 00:30:11,153
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Ready, Fred?
- Ready, George.</font></b>

334
00:30:11,319 --> 00:30:13,155
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Bottoms up.
- Bottoms up.</font></b>

335
00:30:16,575 --> 00:30:18,493
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Yes!
- Yes!</font></b>

336
00:30:19,327 --> 00:30:20,829
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Yeah!</font></b>

337
00:30:21,997 --> 00:30:23,623
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Yes!</font></b>

338
00:30:24,040 --> 00:30:25,542
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Ready?</font></b>

339
00:30:28,837 --> 00:30:31,006
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Yes!
- Yes!</font></b>

340
00:30:39,514 --> 00:30:41,516
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- You said!
- You said!</font></b>

341
00:30:42,476 --> 00:30:45,896
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Oh, right, you want a piece of me?!
- I'll tear your ears off!</font></b>

342
00:30:46,062 --> 00:30:48,565
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Now you're making me laugh.
- Take this! Come on!</font></b>

343
00:30:48,732 --> 00:30:50,192
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Fight! Fight! Fight!</i></font></b>

344
00:30:55,280 --> 00:30:57,032
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">We're "old school," right?</font></b>

345
00:30:57,199 --> 00:30:59,576
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Yeah, but you look older!</font></b>

346
00:31:30,941 --> 00:31:33,610
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Sit down. Please.</font></b>

347
00:31:37,030 --> 00:31:39,908
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Now the moment
you've all been waiting for:</font></b>

348
00:31:40,075 --> 00:31:42,202
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The champion selection.</font></b>

349
00:32:13,608 --> 00:32:17,445
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The Durmstrang champion
is Viktor Krum.</font></b>

350
00:32:33,378 --> 00:32:35,797
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The champion for Beauxbatons...</font></b>

351
00:32:35,964 --> 00:32:37,966
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...is Fleur Delacour.</font></b>

352
00:32:48,518 --> 00:32:51,521
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The Hogwarts champion,
Cedric Diggory!</font></b>

353
00:33:01,573 --> 00:33:05,994
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Excellent! We now have
our three champions.</font></b>

354
00:33:06,161 --> 00:33:10,332
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">But in the end,
only one will go down in history.</font></b>

355
00:33:10,499 --> 00:33:13,835
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Only one will hoist
this chalice of champions...</font></b>

356
00:33:14,169 --> 00:33:17,172
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...this vessel of victory...</font></b>

357
00:33:17,339 --> 00:33:19,549
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...the Triwizard Cup!</font></b>

358
00:33:50,330 --> 00:33:51,998
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Harry Potter.</font></b>

359
00:33:54,084 --> 00:33:55,710
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Harry Potter?</font></b>

360
00:34:00,090 --> 00:34:02,300
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No. No.</font></b>

361
00:34:02,801 --> 00:34:04,094
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Harry Potter!</font></b>

362
00:34:04,553 --> 00:34:06,054
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Go on, Harry.</font></b>

363
00:34:06,221 --> 00:34:07,973
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Harry, for goodness sake.</font></b>

364
00:34:39,463 --> 00:34:40,672
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">He's a cheat!</font></b>

365
00:34:41,214 --> 00:34:43,758
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">He's not even 17 yet!</font></b>

366
00:35:11,620 --> 00:35:15,123
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- It's wrong, I tell you!
- You French tart.</font></b>

367
00:35:15,290 --> 00:35:18,293
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Everything is a conspiracy theory!
- Quiet! I can't think!</font></b>

368
00:35:18,460 --> 00:35:20,462
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Everything is a conspiracy theory!
- I protest.</font></b>

369
00:35:20,629 --> 00:35:21,797
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Harry.
- I protest!</font></b>

370
00:35:21,963 --> 00:35:23,840
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Did you put your name
in the Goblet of Fire?</font></b>

371
00:35:24,007 --> 00:35:26,176
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- No, sir.
- Did you ask one of the older students...</font></b>

372
00:35:26,343 --> 00:35:27,677
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...to do it for you?
- No, sir.</font></b>

373
00:35:27,844 --> 00:35:30,764
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- You're absolutely sure?
- Yes. Yes, sir.</font></b>

374
00:35:31,181 --> 00:35:33,433
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- But of course he is lying.
- The hell he is!</font></b>

375
00:35:33,642 --> 00:35:35,977
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The Goblet of Fire is an exceptionally
powerful magical object.</font></b>

376
00:35:36,144 --> 00:35:39,314
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Only an exceptionally powerful
Confundus Charm could've hoodwinked it.</font></b>

377
00:35:39,481 --> 00:35:41,483
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Magic way beyond the talents
of a fourth year.</font></b>

378
00:35:41,650 --> 00:35:44,653
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You seem to have given this
a fair bit of thought, Mad-Eye.</font></b>

379
00:35:44,820 --> 00:35:47,989
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It was once my job to think
as dark wizards do, Karkaroff...</font></b>

380
00:35:48,156 --> 00:35:51,243
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...perhaps you remember.
- This doesn't help, Alastor.</font></b>

381
00:35:52,994 --> 00:35:55,330
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Leave this to you, Barty.</font></b>

382
00:35:56,665 --> 00:35:58,875
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The rules are absolute.</font></b>

383
00:36:00,085 --> 00:36:03,839
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The Goblet of Fire constitutes
a binding magical contract.</font></b>

384
00:36:05,340 --> 00:36:07,551
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Mr. Potter has no choice.</font></b>

385
00:36:08,343 --> 00:36:10,637
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">He is, as of tonight...</font></b>

386
00:36:12,514 --> 00:36:14,516
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...a Triwizard champion.</font></b>

387
00:36:42,461 --> 00:36:44,588
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">This can't go on, Albus.</font></b>

388
00:36:44,921 --> 00:36:47,757
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">First the Dark Mark. Now this?</font></b>

389
00:36:47,924 --> 00:36:49,926
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What do you suggest, Minerva?</font></b>

390
00:36:51,094 --> 00:36:53,180
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Put an end to it.</font></b>

391
00:36:53,638 --> 00:36:55,640
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Don't let Potter compete.</font></b>

392
00:36:55,807 --> 00:36:58,268
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You heard Barty. The rules are clear.</font></b>

393
00:36:58,435 --> 00:37:01,271
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Well, the devil with Barty
and his rules.</font></b>

394
00:37:01,438 --> 00:37:03,899
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">And since when did you
accommodate the Ministry?</font></b>

395
00:37:04,065 --> 00:37:08,069
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Headmaster, I, too, find it difficult
to believe this mere coincidence.</font></b>

396
00:37:08,236 --> 00:37:12,157
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">However, if we are to truly discover
the meaning of these events...</font></b>

397
00:37:12,324 --> 00:37:15,911
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...perhaps we should,
for the time being...</font></b>

398
00:37:16,828 --> 00:37:19,080
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...let them unfold.</font></b>

399
00:37:19,247 --> 00:37:21,416
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What...? Do nothing?</font></b>

400
00:37:21,583 --> 00:37:23,251
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Offer him up as bait?</font></b>

401
00:37:24,252 --> 00:37:27,088
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Potter is a boy, not a piece of meat.</font></b>

402
00:37:27,964 --> 00:37:30,717
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I agree. With Severus.</font></b>

403
00:37:31,259 --> 00:37:34,095
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Alastor, keep an eye on Harry, will you?</font></b>

404
00:37:34,387 --> 00:37:36,848
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- I can do that.
- Don't let him know, though.</font></b>

405
00:37:37,098 --> 00:37:40,227
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">He must be anxious enough as it is...</font></b>

406
00:37:40,769 --> 00:37:43,438
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...knowing what lies ahead.</font></b>

407
00:37:43,772 --> 00:37:46,358
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Then again, we all are.</font></b>

408
00:38:01,248 --> 00:38:03,041
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">How did you do it?</font></b>

409
00:38:04,501 --> 00:38:07,129
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Never mind. Doesn't matter.</font></b>

410
00:38:07,295 --> 00:38:09,214
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Might've let
your best friend know, though.</font></b>

411
00:38:09,381 --> 00:38:12,634
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Let you know what?
- You know bloody well what.</font></b>

412
00:38:12,801 --> 00:38:15,178
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I didn't ask for this to happen, Ron.</font></b>

413
00:38:15,637 --> 00:38:17,264
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Okay?</font></b>

414
00:38:17,430 --> 00:38:19,933
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- You're being stupid.
- Yeah, that's me.</font></b>

415
00:38:20,100 --> 00:38:23,645
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Ron Weasley,
Harry Potter's stupid friend.</font></b>

416
00:38:27,315 --> 00:38:29,317
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I didn't put my name in that cup.</font></b>

417
00:38:29,734 --> 00:38:33,572
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I don't want eternal glory.
I just wanna be...</font></b>

418
00:38:35,323 --> 00:38:37,784
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Look, I don't know
what happened tonight...</font></b>

419
00:38:37,951 --> 00:38:39,828
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...and I don't know why.</font></b>

420
00:38:39,995 --> 00:38:41,204
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It just did.</font></b>

421
00:38:42,080 --> 00:38:43,665
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Okay?</font></b>

422
00:38:52,466 --> 00:38:54,217
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Piss off.</font></b>

423
00:39:09,232 --> 00:39:11,693
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What a charismatic quartet.</font></b>

424
00:39:13,028 --> 00:39:14,654
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Hello.</font></b>

425
00:39:15,530 --> 00:39:18,074
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I'm Rita Skeeter.</font></b>

426
00:39:18,658 --> 00:39:21,161
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>I write for the Daily Prophet.</i></font></b>

427
00:39:21,745 --> 00:39:26,458
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">But of course you know that, don't you?
It's you we don't know.</font></b>

428
00:39:27,000 --> 00:39:28,835
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You're the juicy news.</font></b>

429
00:39:29,002 --> 00:39:33,215
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What quirks lurk
beneath those rosy cheeks?</font></b>

430
00:39:33,381 --> 00:39:36,885
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What mysteries do the muscles mask?</font></b>

431
00:39:37,052 --> 00:39:40,263
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Does courage lie beneath those curls?</font></b>

432
00:39:40,430 --> 00:39:43,475
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">In short, what makes a champion tick?</font></b>

433
00:39:43,975 --> 00:39:48,271
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">"Me, Myself & l" want to know.
Not to mention my rabid readers.</font></b>

434
00:39:48,438 --> 00:39:50,941
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">So who's feeling up to sharing?</font></b>

435
00:39:54,236 --> 00:39:56,863
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Shall we start with the youngest?
Lovely.</font></b>

436
00:40:09,126 --> 00:40:10,919
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">This is cozy.</font></b>

437
00:40:11,503 --> 00:40:13,213
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It's a broom cupboard.</font></b>

438
00:40:13,588 --> 00:40:15,882
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You should feel right at home, then.</font></b>

439
00:40:16,091 --> 00:40:18,844
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Don't mind if I use
a Quick-Quotes Quill, do you?</font></b>

440
00:40:19,010 --> 00:40:20,595
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No.</font></b>

441
00:40:20,929 --> 00:40:22,931
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">So tell me, Harry.</font></b>

442
00:40:23,098 --> 00:40:26,017
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Here you sit, a mere boy of 12...</font></b>

443
00:40:26,184 --> 00:40:27,686
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I'm 14. Sorry.</font></b>

444
00:40:27,853 --> 00:40:30,814
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- About to compete
against three students...</font></b>

445
00:40:30,981 --> 00:40:34,276
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...not only vastly more
emotionally mature than yourself...</font></b>

446
00:40:34,442 --> 00:40:37,028
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...but who have mastered spells
that you wouldn't attempt...</font></b>

447
00:40:37,195 --> 00:40:39,531
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...in your dizziest daydreams.</font></b>

448
00:40:40,031 --> 00:40:42,075
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Concerned?</font></b>

449
00:40:43,243 --> 00:40:46,079
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I don't know.
I haven't really thought about it.</font></b>

450
00:40:46,246 --> 00:40:48,123
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Just ignore the quill.</font></b>

451
00:40:48,582 --> 00:40:51,126
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Then, of course,
you're no ordinary boy of 12, are you?</font></b>

452
00:40:51,293 --> 00:40:53,879
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Fourteen.
- Your story's legend.</font></b>

453
00:40:54,629 --> 00:40:56,798
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Do you think it was
the trauma of your past...</font></b>

454
00:40:56,965 --> 00:41:00,218
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...that made you so keen to enter
such a dangerous tournament?</font></b>

455
00:41:00,385 --> 00:41:02,137
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No, I didn't enter.</font></b>

456
00:41:02,304 --> 00:41:03,930
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Of course you didn't.</font></b>

457
00:41:06,183 --> 00:41:07,809
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Everyone loves a rebel, Harry.</font></b>

458
00:41:10,145 --> 00:41:11,605
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Scratch that last.</font></b>

459
00:41:12,439 --> 00:41:15,108
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Speaking of your parents,
were they alive...</font></b>

460
00:41:15,275 --> 00:41:16,651
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...how do you think they'd feel?</font></b>

461
00:41:16,818 --> 00:41:18,570
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Proud? Or concerned...</font></b>

462
00:41:18,737 --> 00:41:22,574
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...that your attitude shows, at best,
a pathological need for attention...</font></b>

463
00:41:22,741 --> 00:41:25,327
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...at worst, a psychotic death wish?</font></b>

464
00:41:26,328 --> 00:41:31,416
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Hey, my eyes aren't
"glistening with the ghosts of my past."</font></b>

465
00:42:03,698 --> 00:42:06,034
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Harry, I couldn 't risk sending Hedwig.</i></font></b>

466
00:42:06,201 --> 00:42:09,496
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Since the World Cup, the Ministry's
been intercepting more and more owls...</i></font></b>

467
00:42:09,663 --> 00:42:11,873
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>... and she's too easily recognized.</i></font></b>

468
00:42:12,040 --> 00:42:14,918
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>We need to talk, Harry, face-to-face.</i></font></b>

469
00:42:15,085 --> 00:42:19,256
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Meet me in the Gryffindor common room,
1:00 this Saturday night.</i></font></b>

470
00:42:19,422 --> 00:42:21,216
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>And make sure you're alone.</i></font></b>

471
00:42:21,383 --> 00:42:22,884
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Sirius.</i></font></b>

472
00:42:23,051 --> 00:42:24,553
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>P. S:</i></font></b>

473
00:42:24,719 --> 00:42:26,513
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>The bird bites.</i></font></b>

474
00:42:36,857 --> 00:42:38,275
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Sirius?</font></b>

475
00:42:55,167 --> 00:42:57,085
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Harry Potter, age 12...</i></font></b>

476
00:42:57,252 --> 00:43:00,213
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>... suspect entrant
in the Triwizard Tournament.</i></font></b>

477
00:43:00,380 --> 00:43:02,966
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>His eyes swimming
with the ghosts of his past...</i></font></b>

478
00:43:03,133 --> 00:43:04,718
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>... and choking back tears...</i></font></b>

479
00:43:20,192 --> 00:43:22,777
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Sirius. How...?</font></b>

480
00:43:22,944 --> 00:43:25,447
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I don't have much time,
so let me get straight to it.</font></b>

481
00:43:25,614 --> 00:43:28,575
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Did you or did you not put your name
into the Goblet of Fire?</font></b>

482
00:43:28,742 --> 00:43:30,202
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No!</font></b>

483
00:43:30,786 --> 00:43:32,078
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I had to ask.</font></b>

484
00:43:32,245 --> 00:43:37,042
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Now, tell me about this dream of yours.
You mentioned Wormtail and Voldemort.</font></b>

485
00:43:37,209 --> 00:43:39,628
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">But who was the third man in the room?</font></b>

486
00:43:39,795 --> 00:43:42,297
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- I don't know.
- You didn't hear a name?</font></b>

487
00:43:43,131 --> 00:43:44,674
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No.</font></b>

488
00:43:45,592 --> 00:43:49,304
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Voldemort was giving him a job to do.
Something important.</font></b>

489
00:43:49,471 --> 00:43:50,764
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">And what was that?</font></b>

490
00:43:52,974 --> 00:43:54,601
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">He wanted...</font></b>

491
00:43:54,768 --> 00:43:56,436
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...me.</font></b>

492
00:43:56,978 --> 00:44:01,316
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I don't know why. But he was
gonna use this man to get to me.</font></b>

493
00:44:02,609 --> 00:44:04,694
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">But, I mean, it was only a dream, right?</font></b>

494
00:44:05,153 --> 00:44:06,780
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Yes.</font></b>

495
00:44:06,947 --> 00:44:08,490
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It's just a dream.</font></b>

496
00:44:09,241 --> 00:44:10,659
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Look, Harry.</font></b>

497
00:44:10,826 --> 00:44:14,329
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The Death Eaters at the World Cup,
your name rising from that goblet...</font></b>

498
00:44:14,496 --> 00:44:18,500
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...these are not just coincidences.
Hogwarts isn't safe anymore.</font></b>

499
00:44:18,667 --> 00:44:19,751
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What are you saying?</font></b>

500
00:44:19,918 --> 00:44:24,172
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I'm saying the devils are inside
the walls. Igor Karkaroff?</font></b>

501
00:44:24,339 --> 00:44:28,718
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">He was a Death Eater. And no one,
no one stops being a Death Eater.</font></b>

502
00:44:29,177 --> 00:44:31,721
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Then there's Barty Crouch.
Heart of stone.</font></b>

503
00:44:31,888 --> 00:44:34,266
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Sent his own son to Azkaban.</font></b>

504
00:44:39,146 --> 00:44:41,231
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You think one of them
put my name in the goblet?</font></b>

505
00:44:41,398 --> 00:44:43,692
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I haven't a clue who put your name
in that goblet...</font></b>

506
00:44:43,859 --> 00:44:47,863
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...but whoever did is no friend to you.
People die in this tournament.</font></b>

507
00:44:48,029 --> 00:44:51,450
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- I'm not ready for this, Sirius.
- You don't have a choice.</font></b>

508
00:44:55,036 --> 00:44:57,456
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Someone's coming.
- Keep your friends close, Harry.</font></b>

509
00:45:00,750 --> 00:45:02,711
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Who were you talking to?
- What?</font></b>

510
00:45:02,878 --> 00:45:05,297
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Who says I was talking to anyone?
- I heard voices.</font></b>

511
00:45:05,589 --> 00:45:09,593
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Maybe you're imagining things.
Wouldn't be the first time.</font></b>

512
00:45:10,135 --> 00:45:13,472
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You're probably just practicing
for your next interview, I expect.</font></b>

513
00:45:39,414 --> 00:45:41,041
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Amazing.</font></b>

514
00:45:43,001 --> 00:45:46,713
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Amazing!
- Neville. You're doing it again.</font></b>

515
00:45:47,255 --> 00:45:48,673
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Right, sorry.</font></b>

516
00:45:49,549 --> 00:45:52,552
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>"Magical Water Plants
of the Highland Lochs"?</i></font></b>

517
00:45:52,719 --> 00:45:55,889
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Moody gave it to me.
That day we had tea.</font></b>

518
00:45:57,390 --> 00:45:59,100
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It's already been through enough people.</font></b>

519
00:45:59,267 --> 00:46:01,394
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Why don't you just go
and talk to him yourself?</font></b>

520
00:46:02,854 --> 00:46:05,190
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Ron, this is your problem, not mine.</font></b>

521
00:46:05,357 --> 00:46:07,442
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What do you want me to say again?</font></b>

522
00:46:07,609 --> 00:46:08,944
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Go.</font></b>

523
00:46:11,905 --> 00:46:15,992
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Ronald would like me to tell you
that Seamus told him...</font></b>

524
00:46:16,618 --> 00:46:20,247
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...that Dean was told by Parvati
that Hagrid's looking for you.</font></b>

525
00:46:20,413 --> 00:46:22,833
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Is that right? Well, you...</font></b>

526
00:46:22,999 --> 00:46:24,084
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What?</font></b>

527
00:46:29,172 --> 00:46:32,134
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Are you sure you won't do this?
- Do it.</font></b>

528
00:46:34,928 --> 00:46:37,889
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Dean was told by Parvati that...</font></b>

529
00:46:39,141 --> 00:46:41,351
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Please don't ask me to say it again.</font></b>

530
00:46:41,726 --> 00:46:43,186
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Hagrid's looking for you.</font></b>

531
00:46:43,687 --> 00:46:46,773
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Well, you can tell Ronald...
- I'm not an owl!</font></b>

532
00:46:57,325 --> 00:46:59,578
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Did you bring your father's cloak,
like I asked you?</font></b>

533
00:46:59,744 --> 00:47:02,330
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Yeah, I brought the cloak.
Hagrid, where are we going?</font></b>

534
00:47:02,497 --> 00:47:03,915
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You'll see soon enough.</font></b>

535
00:47:04,082 --> 00:47:06,293
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Now pay attention, this is important.</font></b>

536
00:47:08,003 --> 00:47:09,421
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What's with the flower?</font></b>

537
00:47:10,505 --> 00:47:12,924
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Hagrid, have you combed your hair?</font></b>

538
00:47:13,341 --> 00:47:15,051
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">As a matter of fact, I have.</font></b>

539
00:47:15,510 --> 00:47:18,430
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You might like to try the same thing
now and again.</font></b>

540
00:47:26,938 --> 00:47:28,398
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Hagrid?</font></b>

541
00:47:32,319 --> 00:47:34,154
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The cloak! Put the cloak on!</font></b>

542
00:47:40,744 --> 00:47:44,164
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>- Bonsoir, Olympe.
- Oh, Hagrid.</i></font></b>

543
00:47:44,331 --> 00:47:48,043
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I thought perhaps you weren't coming.
I thought perhaps...</font></b>

544
00:47:48,210 --> 00:47:50,879
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...you had forgotten me.</font></b>

545
00:47:51,046 --> 00:47:53,006
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Couldn't forget you, Olympe.</font></b>

546
00:47:53,673 --> 00:47:55,425
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What is it you wanted to show me?</font></b>

547
00:47:57,177 --> 00:48:00,388
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">When we spoke earlier,
you sounded so...</font></b>

548
00:48:00,722 --> 00:48:02,224
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...exhilarated.</font></b>

549
00:48:02,808 --> 00:48:05,644
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You'll be glad you came. Trust me.</font></b>

550
00:48:16,238 --> 00:48:17,989
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Can we get closer?</font></b>

551
00:48:25,789 --> 00:48:27,249
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Dragons?</font></b>

552
00:48:27,415 --> 00:48:28,917
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">That's the first task?</font></b>

553
00:48:29,334 --> 00:48:31,294
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- You're joking.
- Come on, Harry.</font></b>

554
00:48:32,629 --> 00:48:35,674
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">These are seriously
misunderstood creatures.</font></b>

555
00:48:36,758 --> 00:48:38,260
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Oh, crikey!</font></b>

556
00:48:38,802 --> 00:48:40,887
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Although, I have to admit...</font></b>

557
00:48:41,054 --> 00:48:43,890
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...that Horntail is a right nasty
piece of work.</font></b>

558
00:48:44,057 --> 00:48:46,810
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Poor Ron nearly fainted
just seeing him, you know.</font></b>

559
00:48:48,395 --> 00:48:50,438
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Ron was here?
- Oh, sure.</font></b>

560
00:48:50,605 --> 00:48:54,109
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">His brother Charlie helped
to bring him over from Romania.</font></b>

561
00:48:54,276 --> 00:48:55,652
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Didn't Ron tell you that?</font></b>

562
00:48:57,654 --> 00:48:59,072
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No, he didn't.</font></b>

563
00:48:59,781 --> 00:49:01,658
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">He didn't tell me a thing.</font></b>

564
00:49:11,626 --> 00:49:14,713
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- You cheat, Potter.
- You stink, Potter.</font></b>

565
00:49:16,214 --> 00:49:18,884
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Good luck, Potter.
- Potter stinks!</font></b>

566
00:49:19,050 --> 00:49:21,720
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Cedric rules.
- Thanks.</font></b>

567
00:49:22,804 --> 00:49:24,473
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Like the badge?</font></b>

568
00:49:25,015 --> 00:49:26,766
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Excuse me.</font></b>

569
00:49:30,937 --> 00:49:32,397
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Harry.</font></b>

570
00:49:32,981 --> 00:49:34,941
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Hey! Read the badge, Potter!</font></b>

571
00:49:35,108 --> 00:49:36,610
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Can I have a word?</font></b>

572
00:49:37,569 --> 00:49:39,446
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- All right.
- You stink, Potter!</font></b>

573
00:49:39,613 --> 00:49:42,616
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Potter, you stink!
- Harry Potter smells!</font></b>

574
00:49:45,118 --> 00:49:47,662
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Dragons. That's the first task.</font></b>

575
00:49:47,829 --> 00:49:50,999
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- They've got one for each of us.
- Come on, Ced!</font></b>

576
00:49:51,166 --> 00:49:53,168
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Are you serious?</font></b>

577
00:49:53,960 --> 00:49:57,005
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">And Fleur and Krum, do they...?</font></b>

578
00:49:57,172 --> 00:49:59,424
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Yes.
- Come on, Ced, leave him.</font></b>

579
00:49:59,591 --> 00:50:01,051
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Right.
- He's not worth it.</font></b>

580
00:50:01,218 --> 00:50:03,720
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Read the badges, Potter!
- Hey, listen. About the badges.</font></b>

581
00:50:03,887 --> 00:50:06,932
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- I've asked them not to wear them, but...
- Don't worry about it.</font></b>

582
00:50:07,098 --> 00:50:09,518
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It's not like I try
to blow things up, exactly.</font></b>

583
00:50:10,227 --> 00:50:11,686
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It just happens a fair bit.</font></b>

584
00:50:11,853 --> 00:50:14,940
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You have to admit, though,
fire's pretty fascinating.</font></b>

585
00:50:15,106 --> 00:50:16,983
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You're a right foul git, you know that?</font></b>

586
00:50:17,150 --> 00:50:19,361
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- You think so?
- I know so.</font></b>

587
00:50:19,528 --> 00:50:20,862
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Anything else?</font></b>

588
00:50:21,029 --> 00:50:24,533
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Yeah. Stay away from me.
- Fine.</font></b>

589
00:50:26,910 --> 00:50:30,539
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- There's Potter. Cheat.
- Why so tense, Potter?</font></b>

590
00:50:31,289 --> 00:50:33,708
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">My father and I have a bet, you see.</font></b>

591
00:50:33,875 --> 00:50:37,045
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I don't think you're gonna last
10 minutes in this tournament.</font></b>

592
00:50:39,631 --> 00:50:42,551
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">He disagrees.
He thinks you won't last five.</font></b>

593
00:50:42,717 --> 00:50:45,846
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I don't give a damn
what your father thinks, Malfoy.</font></b>

594
00:50:46,847 --> 00:50:50,851
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">He's vile and cruel.
And you're just pathetic.</font></b>

595
00:50:51,768 --> 00:50:54,271
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Pathetic?
- Oh, no, you don't, sonny!</font></b>

596
00:50:56,523 --> 00:50:59,401
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I'll teach you to curse someone
when their back is turned!</font></b>

597
00:50:59,568 --> 00:51:03,405
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You stinking, cowardly, scummy...</font></b>

598
00:51:03,572 --> 00:51:05,323
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Professor Moody!
...back-shooting...</font></b>

599
00:51:05,490 --> 00:51:08,410
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- What are you doing?
- Teaching.</font></b>

600
00:51:09,411 --> 00:51:13,582
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Is that a...? Is that a student?
- Technically, it's a ferret.</font></b>

601
00:51:19,254 --> 00:51:21,131
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Stand still! Stand still!</font></b>

602
00:51:32,100 --> 00:51:34,311
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- My father will hear about this!
- Is that a threat?</font></b>

603
00:51:34,478 --> 00:51:36,438
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Professor Moody!
- Is that a threat?</font></b>

604
00:51:36,605 --> 00:51:38,440
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Professor!</font></b>

605
00:51:38,607 --> 00:51:42,194
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I could tell you stories about your father
that would curl even your greasy hair!</font></b>

606
00:51:42,360 --> 00:51:45,071
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Alastor! Alastor.
- It doesn't end here!</font></b>

607
00:51:45,238 --> 00:51:49,034
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">We never use transfiguration
as a punishment!</font></b>

608
00:51:49,201 --> 00:51:51,411
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Surely Dumbledore told you that.</font></b>

609
00:51:51,953 --> 00:51:56,416
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- He might've mentioned it.
- Well, you will do well to remember it.</font></b>

610
00:51:57,501 --> 00:51:58,960
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Away!</font></b>

611
00:52:02,088 --> 00:52:04,299
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You. Come with me.</font></b>

612
00:52:39,501 --> 00:52:41,586
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">That's a Foe-Glass.</font></b>

613
00:52:42,337 --> 00:52:44,422
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Lets me keep an eye on my enemies.</font></b>

614
00:52:44,881 --> 00:52:49,302
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">If I can see the whites of their eyes,
they're standing right behind me.</font></b>

615
00:52:53,473 --> 00:52:55,934
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Wouldn't even bother telling you
what's in there.</font></b>

616
00:52:56,101 --> 00:52:58,145
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You wouldn't believe it if I did.</font></b>

617
00:52:58,395 --> 00:53:00,105
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Now...</font></b>

618
00:53:01,773 --> 00:53:04,609
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...what are you going to do
about your dragon?</font></b>

619
00:53:08,530 --> 00:53:10,824
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Well, you know, I just thought I'd...</font></b>

620
00:53:12,284 --> 00:53:13,785
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Sit.</font></b>

621
00:53:17,497 --> 00:53:18,874
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Listen to me, Potter.</font></b>

622
00:53:19,875 --> 00:53:21,042
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Your pal Diggory?</font></b>

623
00:53:21,209 --> 00:53:25,630
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">By your age, he could turn a whistle into
a watch and have it sing you the time.</font></b>

624
00:53:26,840 --> 00:53:28,091
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Miss Delacour?</font></b>

625
00:53:28,508 --> 00:53:31,219
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">She's as much a fairy princess as I am.</font></b>

626
00:53:31,720 --> 00:53:35,307
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">As for Krum, his head
may be filled with sawdust...</font></b>

627
00:53:35,474 --> 00:53:37,642
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...but Karkaroff's is not.</font></b>

628
00:53:37,809 --> 00:53:39,644
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">They'll have a strategy.</font></b>

629
00:53:39,811 --> 00:53:43,273
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">And you can bet that it will
play to Krum's strengths.</font></b>

630
00:53:48,111 --> 00:53:49,696
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Come on, Potter.</font></b>

631
00:53:49,863 --> 00:53:51,948
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What are your strengths?</font></b>

632
00:53:53,533 --> 00:53:54,910
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I don't know.</font></b>

633
00:53:55,076 --> 00:53:57,871
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Well, I can fly.
I mean, I'm a fair flyer. But I...</font></b>

634
00:53:58,038 --> 00:54:02,083
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Better than fair, the way I heard it.
- But I'm not allowed a broom.</font></b>

635
00:54:02,250 --> 00:54:05,879
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You're allowed a wand.</font></b>

636
00:54:12,302 --> 00:54:13,762
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Bets! Place your bets!</font></b>

637
00:54:13,929 --> 00:54:16,097
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Bets taken! Bets taken here!</font></b>

638
00:54:16,264 --> 00:54:19,226
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Step up, folks! Who fancies a flutter
in today's bloodbath?</font></b>

639
00:54:19,392 --> 00:54:22,187
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Smart money's on Krum to survive!
Any bets?</font></b>

640
00:54:22,437 --> 00:54:23,939
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Yes, sir?</font></b>

641
00:54:24,272 --> 00:54:26,942
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Ten-to-1 for Fleur. There you go.
Thank you very much.</font></b>

642
00:54:27,484 --> 00:54:29,444
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Your attention, please.</i></font></b>

643
00:54:29,653 --> 00:54:32,280
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>This is a great day for all of us.</i></font></b>

644
00:54:35,700 --> 00:54:39,955
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Each of the three tasks involves
very considerable danger.</i></font></b>

645
00:54:40,122 --> 00:54:42,791
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Please keep your seats at all times.</i></font></b>

646
00:54:42,958 --> 00:54:45,710
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>This will minimize any risks
you may be exposed to.</i></font></b>

647
00:54:45,877 --> 00:54:49,297
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Harry? Is that you?
- Yeah.</font></b>

648
00:54:49,464 --> 00:54:51,174
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>I'm sure we all wish our champions...</i></font></b>

649
00:54:51,341 --> 00:54:54,427
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>- How are you feeling? Okay?
- ... the greatest of luck.</i></font></b>

650
00:54:56,721 --> 00:55:00,142
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The key is to concentrate.
After that, you just have to...</font></b>

651
00:55:00,308 --> 00:55:02,144
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Battle a dragon.</font></b>

652
00:55:06,439 --> 00:55:08,900
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Young love.</font></b>

653
00:55:09,651 --> 00:55:10,902
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">How...</font></b>

654
00:55:13,363 --> 00:55:14,656
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...stirring.</font></b>

655
00:55:17,325 --> 00:55:20,495
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">If everything goes unfortunately today...</font></b>

656
00:55:20,662 --> 00:55:23,457
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...you two may even
make the front page.</font></b>

657
00:55:23,623 --> 00:55:25,834
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You have no business here.</font></b>

658
00:55:26,001 --> 00:55:28,003
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">This tent is for champions...</font></b>

659
00:55:28,378 --> 00:55:30,088
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...and friends.</font></b>

660
00:55:32,883 --> 00:55:37,053
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No matter. We've got what we wanted.</font></b>

661
00:55:40,182 --> 00:55:43,018
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Good day, champions.
Gather round, please.</font></b>

662
00:55:43,185 --> 00:55:47,355
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Now, you've waited, you've wondered,
and at last the moment has arrived.</font></b>

663
00:55:47,522 --> 00:55:50,775
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">A moment only four of you
can fully appreciate.</font></b>

664
00:55:50,942 --> 00:55:53,069
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What are you doing here, Miss Granger?</font></b>

665
00:55:54,362 --> 00:55:56,031
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Sorry, I'll just go.</font></b>

666
00:55:56,198 --> 00:55:57,741
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Barty, the bag.</font></b>

667
00:55:58,200 --> 00:56:00,410
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Champions, in a circle around me.</font></b>

668
00:56:00,577 --> 00:56:03,705
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Miss Delacour, over here. Mr. Krum.</font></b>

669
00:56:03,872 --> 00:56:07,793
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">And, Potter, Mr. Potter, over here.
That's right. Now...</font></b>

670
00:56:07,959 --> 00:56:10,378
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...Miss Delacour, if you will.</font></b>

671
00:56:14,466 --> 00:56:16,134
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The Welsh Green.</font></b>

672
00:56:20,764 --> 00:56:22,057
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Mr. Krum.</font></b>

673
00:56:25,060 --> 00:56:26,978
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The Chinese Fireball.</font></b>

674
00:56:33,443 --> 00:56:35,862
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The Swedish Short-Snout.</font></b>

675
00:56:36,321 --> 00:56:38,323
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Which leaves...
- The Horntail.</font></b>

676
00:56:38,490 --> 00:56:40,742
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- What's that, boy?
- Nothing.</font></b>

677
00:56:44,162 --> 00:56:46,581
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The Hungarian Horntail.</font></b>

678
00:56:48,750 --> 00:56:51,878
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">These represent four
very real dragons...</font></b>

679
00:56:52,045 --> 00:56:55,090
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...each of which has been given
a golden egg to protect.</font></b>

680
00:56:55,257 --> 00:56:57,759
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Your objective is simple:</font></b>

681
00:56:57,926 --> 00:56:59,427
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Collect the egg.</font></b>

682
00:56:59,594 --> 00:57:02,597
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">This you must do,
for each egg contains a clue...</font></b>

683
00:57:02,764 --> 00:57:06,268
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...without which you cannot hope
to proceed to the next task.</font></b>

684
00:57:06,434 --> 00:57:07,769
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Any questions?</font></b>

685
00:57:08,770 --> 00:57:11,439
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Very well. Good luck, champions.</font></b>

686
00:57:11,606 --> 00:57:14,401
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Mr. Diggory, at the sound of the cannon,
you may...</font></b>

687
00:57:23,076 --> 00:57:26,913
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Diggory! Diggory! Diggory!</i></font></b>

688
00:57:38,467 --> 00:57:41,845
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Three of our champions
have now faced their dragons...</i></font></b>

689
00:57:42,012 --> 00:57:45,515
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>... and so each one of them
will proceed to the next task.</i></font></b>

690
00:57:46,099 --> 00:57:49,186
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>And now our fourth
and final contestant.</i></font></b>

691
00:57:51,146 --> 00:57:54,733
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Harry! Harry! Harry!</i></font></b>

692
00:59:01,842 --> 00:59:04,761
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Your wand, Harry! Your wand!</font></b>

693
00:59:05,262 --> 00:59:07,305
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Accio Firebolt!</i></font></b>

694
00:59:36,293 --> 00:59:38,462
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Yeah!
- Yes!</font></b>

695
00:59:47,387 --> 00:59:48,805
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Oh, my God.</font></b>

696
00:59:58,440 --> 01:00:01,735
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Yeah!
- Yeah! Well done, dragon!</font></b>

697
01:02:33,762 --> 01:02:35,931
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Yes! Yes!</font></b>

698
01:02:59,121 --> 01:03:01,832
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Yes, Harry!
- Knew you wouldn't die. Lose a leg.</font></b>

699
01:03:01,998 --> 01:03:03,959
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Or an arm.
- Pack it in altogether?</font></b>

700
01:03:04,126 --> 01:03:05,877
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Never!
- Never!</font></b>

701
01:03:07,963 --> 01:03:09,297
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Shush!</font></b>

702
01:03:09,798 --> 01:03:12,467
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Go on, Harry. What's the clue?</font></b>

703
01:03:13,468 --> 01:03:16,304
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Who wants me to open it?
- Yes!</font></b>

704
01:03:17,139 --> 01:03:19,641
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Do you want me to open it?
- Yes!</font></b>

705
01:03:30,819 --> 01:03:33,238
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What the bloody hell was that?</font></b>

706
01:03:37,367 --> 01:03:40,120
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">All right, everyone!
Go back to your knitting.</font></b>

707
01:03:40,287 --> 01:03:44,332
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">This is gonna be uncomfortable enough
without all you nosy sods listening in.</font></b>

708
01:03:47,502 --> 01:03:51,423
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I reckon you have to be barking mad to
put your own name in the Goblet of Fire.</font></b>

709
01:03:51,840 --> 01:03:54,551
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Caught on, have you?
Took you long enough.</font></b>

710
01:03:55,677 --> 01:03:57,804
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I wasn't the only one
who thought you'd done it.</font></b>

711
01:03:57,971 --> 01:04:00,223
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Everyone was saying it
behind your back.</font></b>

712
01:04:02,434 --> 01:04:05,687
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Brilliant.
That makes me feel loads better.</font></b>

713
01:04:06,605 --> 01:04:09,983
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Least I warned you about the dragons.
- Hagrid warned me about the dragons.</font></b>

714
01:04:10,150 --> 01:04:11,651
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No, no, no, I did.</font></b>

715
01:04:11,818 --> 01:04:14,863
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No, don't you remember?
I told Hermione to tell you...</font></b>

716
01:04:15,030 --> 01:04:19,075
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...that Seamus told me that Parvati
told Dean that Hagrid was looking for you.</font></b>

717
01:04:19,242 --> 01:04:23,205
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Seamus never actually told me anything,
so it was really me all along.</font></b>

718
01:04:24,206 --> 01:04:27,209
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I thought we'd be all right, you know...</font></b>

719
01:04:27,417 --> 01:04:29,419
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...after you'd figured that out.</font></b>

720
01:04:29,795 --> 01:04:32,464
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Who...? Who could possibly
figure that out?</font></b>

721
01:04:33,131 --> 01:04:34,549
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">That's completely mental.</font></b>

722
01:04:34,716 --> 01:04:37,761
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Yeah. Isn't it?</font></b>

723
01:04:37,928 --> 01:04:39,971
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I suppose I was a bit distraught.</font></b>

724
01:04:42,557 --> 01:04:44,267
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Boys.</font></b>

725
01:05:08,750 --> 01:05:10,168
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Hi, Harry.
- Hi, Harry.</font></b>

726
01:05:13,797 --> 01:05:16,424
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Cho, Harry's looking at you.</font></b>

727
01:05:20,345 --> 01:05:22,055
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Shush.</font></b>

728
01:05:22,764 --> 01:05:24,099
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Look at this!</font></b>

729
01:05:26,101 --> 01:05:28,603
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I can't believe it! She's done it again.</font></b>

730
01:05:29,646 --> 01:05:31,898
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">"Miss Granger,
a plain but ambitious girl...</font></b>

731
01:05:32,065 --> 01:05:34,818
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...seems to be developing a taste
for famous wizards.</font></b>

732
01:05:34,985 --> 01:05:37,279
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Her latest prey, sources report...</font></b>

733
01:05:37,446 --> 01:05:41,074
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...is none other than the
Bulgarian bonbon, Viktor Krum.</font></b>

734
01:05:41,366 --> 01:05:45,287
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No word yet on how Harry Potter's
taking this latest emotional blow."</font></b>

735
01:05:46,663 --> 01:05:48,623
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Parcel for you, Mr. Weasley.</font></b>

736
01:05:48,790 --> 01:05:50,292
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Thank you, Nigel.</font></b>

737
01:05:55,088 --> 01:05:57,924
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Not now, Nigel. Later.</font></b>

738
01:05:59,759 --> 01:06:01,303
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Go on.</font></b>

739
01:06:06,641 --> 01:06:09,394
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I told him I'd get him Harry's autograph.</font></b>

740
01:06:11,605 --> 01:06:13,356
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Oh, look, Mum's sent me something.</font></b>

741
01:06:21,490 --> 01:06:23,325
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Mum sent me a dress.</font></b>

742
01:06:23,492 --> 01:06:27,329
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Well, it does match your eyes.
Is there a bonnet?</font></b>

743
01:06:27,788 --> 01:06:29,623
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Nose down, Harry.</font></b>

744
01:06:30,165 --> 01:06:34,044
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Ginny, these must be for you.
- I'm not wearing that, it's ghastly.</font></b>

745
01:06:35,837 --> 01:06:37,672
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What are you on about?</font></b>

746
01:06:37,839 --> 01:06:39,800
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">They're not for Ginny.</font></b>

747
01:06:39,966 --> 01:06:41,301
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">They're for you.</font></b>

748
01:06:42,344 --> 01:06:46,097
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Dress robes.
- Dress robes? For what?</font></b>

749
01:06:47,349 --> 01:06:49,518
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The Yule Ball...</font></b>

750
01:06:49,684 --> 01:06:55,023
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...has been a tradition
of the Triwizard Tournament...</font></b>

751
01:06:55,732 --> 01:06:57,818
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...since its inception.</font></b>

752
01:06:58,485 --> 01:07:02,364
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">On Christmas Eve night,
we and our guests...</font></b>

753
01:07:02,531 --> 01:07:04,199
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...gather in the Great Hall...</font></b>

754
01:07:04,366 --> 01:07:08,411
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...for a night of well-mannered frivolity.</font></b>

755
01:07:09,955 --> 01:07:12,207
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">As representatives of the host school...</font></b>

756
01:07:12,374 --> 01:07:17,420
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...I expect each and every one of you
to put your best foot forward.</font></b>

757
01:07:17,796 --> 01:07:20,423
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">And I mean this literally, because...</font></b>

758
01:07:20,590 --> 01:07:25,053
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...the Yule Ball is, first and foremost...</font></b>

759
01:07:25,887 --> 01:07:27,389
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...a dance.</font></b>

760
01:07:31,643 --> 01:07:33,436
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Silence!</font></b>

761
01:07:33,645 --> 01:07:36,648
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The house of Godric Gryffindor
has commanded the respect...</font></b>

762
01:07:36,815 --> 01:07:39,443
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...of the wizard world
for nearly 10 centuries.</font></b>

763
01:07:39,609 --> 01:07:43,697
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I will not have you, in the course of a
single evening, besmirching that name...</font></b>

764
01:07:43,864 --> 01:07:48,076
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...by behaving like a babbling,
bumbling band of baboons.</font></b>

765
01:07:48,785 --> 01:07:50,745
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Try saying that five times fast, huh?</font></b>

766
01:07:50,912 --> 01:07:52,414
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Now, to dance...</font></b>

767
01:07:52,581 --> 01:07:56,293
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...is to let the body breathe.</font></b>

768
01:07:56,460 --> 01:07:59,796
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Inside every girl,
a secret swan slumbers...</font></b>

769
01:07:59,963 --> 01:08:02,340
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...Ionging to burst forth
and take flight.</font></b>

770
01:08:02,507 --> 01:08:06,511
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Something's about to burst out of Eloise
Midgen, but I don't think it's a swan.</font></b>

771
01:08:06,678 --> 01:08:09,806
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Inside every boy,
a lordly lion prepared to prance.</font></b>

772
01:08:09,973 --> 01:08:12,225
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Mr. Weasley.
- Yes?</font></b>

773
01:08:12,392 --> 01:08:14,811
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Will you join me, please?</font></b>

774
01:08:19,441 --> 01:08:22,944
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Now, place your right hand
on my waist.</font></b>

775
01:08:23,111 --> 01:08:25,697
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Where?
- My waist.</font></b>

776
01:08:25,864 --> 01:08:28,408
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">And extend your arm.</font></b>

777
01:08:28,867 --> 01:08:30,827
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Mr. Filch, if you please.</font></b>

778
01:08:33,914 --> 01:08:35,916
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">One, two, three.</font></b>

779
01:08:36,082 --> 01:08:39,586
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">One, two, three. One, two, three.</font></b>

780
01:08:43,298 --> 01:08:45,425
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Never gonna let him forget this,
are you?</font></b>

781
01:08:45,592 --> 01:08:46,760
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Never.
- Never.</font></b>

782
01:08:46,927 --> 01:08:50,806
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Everybody come together.
Boys, on your feet!</font></b>

783
01:09:13,870 --> 01:09:15,831
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Why do they have to travel in packs?</font></b>

784
01:09:15,997 --> 01:09:18,625
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">How are you supposed to get one
on their own to ask them?</font></b>

785
01:09:26,508 --> 01:09:30,011
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Blimey, Harry. You've slayed dragons.
If you can't get a date, who can?</font></b>

786
01:09:30,178 --> 01:09:32,430
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I think I'd take the dragon right now.</font></b>

787
01:09:38,645 --> 01:09:40,188
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I take after my mum.</font></b>

788
01:09:40,355 --> 01:09:44,317
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Though I didn't know her very well.
She left when I was about 3.</font></b>

789
01:09:44,484 --> 01:09:46,403
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No, not the maternal sort, her.</font></b>

790
01:09:46,570 --> 01:09:50,157
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Broke me dad's heart, though.
He was a tiny little fella, my dad.</font></b>

791
01:09:50,323 --> 01:09:54,870
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I could pick him up at the age of 6 with
one hand and put him up on the dresser.</font></b>

792
01:09:55,036 --> 01:09:57,372
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">He laughed so hard at that.</font></b>

793
01:09:59,416 --> 01:10:01,293
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Very funny.</font></b>

794
01:10:07,215 --> 01:10:10,969
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">And then he died
just when I started school, so...</font></b>

795
01:10:11,136 --> 01:10:14,181
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">So I sort of had to make
me own way, as it were.</font></b>

796
01:10:14,598 --> 01:10:16,766
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">But enough of me. What about you?</font></b>

797
01:10:34,034 --> 01:10:39,122
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">This is mad. At this rate, we'll be
the only ones in our year without dates.</font></b>

798
01:10:41,416 --> 01:10:44,127
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Well, us and Neville.</font></b>

799
01:10:44,294 --> 01:10:46,963
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Yeah, but, then again,
he can take himself.</font></b>

800
01:10:47,714 --> 01:10:51,051
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It might interest you to know
that Neville's already got someone.</font></b>

801
01:10:53,512 --> 01:10:55,263
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Now I'm really depressed.</font></b>

802
01:11:01,102 --> 01:11:04,523
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">"Get a move on or all the good ones
will have gone."</font></b>

803
01:11:06,608 --> 01:11:08,610
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Who you going with, then?</font></b>

804
01:11:11,321 --> 01:11:13,031
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>- Oi, Angelina?
- What?</i></font></b>

805
01:11:13,198 --> 01:11:18,495
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Do you wanna go to the ball with me?</font></b>

806
01:11:18,829 --> 01:11:20,580
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">To the ball?</font></b>

807
01:11:20,747 --> 01:11:22,165
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Yeah, all right.</font></b>

808
01:11:25,919 --> 01:11:27,462
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Oi, Hermione.</font></b>

809
01:11:27,629 --> 01:11:29,297
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You're a girl.</font></b>

810
01:11:29,464 --> 01:11:30,799
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Very well spotted.</font></b>

811
01:11:30,966 --> 01:11:32,884
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Come with one of us?</font></b>

812
01:11:37,514 --> 01:11:40,433
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Come on. It's one thing for a bloke
to show up alone.</font></b>

813
01:11:40,600 --> 01:11:42,102
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">For a girl, it's just sad.</font></b>

814
01:11:42,269 --> 01:11:46,022
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I won't be going alone, because,
believe it or not, someone's asked me!</font></b>

815
01:11:52,988 --> 01:11:54,990
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">And I said yes!</font></b>

816
01:11:56,825 --> 01:11:58,410
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Bloody hell.</font></b>

817
01:11:58,577 --> 01:12:00,245
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">She's lying, right?</font></b>

818
01:12:00,412 --> 01:12:01,621
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">If you say so.</font></b>

819
01:12:02,330 --> 01:12:05,667
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Look, we've just gotta
grit our teeth and do it.</font></b>

820
01:12:05,834 --> 01:12:07,919
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Tonight, when we get back
to the common room...</font></b>

821
01:12:08,086 --> 01:12:09,796
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...we'll both have partners. Agreed?</font></b>

822
01:12:09,963 --> 01:12:11,465
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Agreed.</font></b>

823
01:12:35,822 --> 01:12:37,157
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Cho!
- Harry!</font></b>

824
01:12:40,702 --> 01:12:43,455
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Watch yourself on the stairs.
It's a bit icy at the top.</font></b>

825
01:12:43,622 --> 01:12:45,207
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Okay, thanks.</font></b>

826
01:12:49,669 --> 01:12:50,712
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Cho?</font></b>

827
01:12:51,671 --> 01:12:53,215
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Yes?</font></b>

828
01:12:54,591 --> 01:12:56,843
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Well, I just wondered if you...</font></b>

829
01:12:57,010 --> 01:12:59,763
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I wondered if maybe
you wanted to go to the ball with me.</font></b>

830
01:13:01,473 --> 01:13:03,725
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Sorry, I didn't catch that.</font></b>

831
01:13:04,643 --> 01:13:09,564
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I was just wondering if maybe
you wanted to go to the ball with me.</font></b>

832
01:13:15,570 --> 01:13:17,155
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Harry...</font></b>

833
01:13:17,322 --> 01:13:20,158
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...I'm sorry, but someone's
already asked me.</font></b>

834
01:13:21,159 --> 01:13:22,577
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">And...</font></b>

835
01:13:23,245 --> 01:13:26,498
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Well, I've said I'll go with him.</font></b>

836
01:13:28,166 --> 01:13:30,669
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Okay. Yeah. Great.</font></b>

837
01:13:32,045 --> 01:13:34,756
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Fine. No problem.</font></b>

838
01:13:35,090 --> 01:13:36,675
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Okay. Good.</font></b>

839
01:13:38,135 --> 01:13:39,678
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Harry?</font></b>

840
01:13:40,303 --> 01:13:42,097
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I really am...</font></b>

841
01:13:42,264 --> 01:13:43,932
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...sorry.</font></b>

842
01:13:53,692 --> 01:13:55,193
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It's all right, Ron.</font></b>

843
01:13:55,360 --> 01:13:58,572
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It's okay, Ron. It's all right.
It doesn't matter.</font></b>

844
01:13:58,738 --> 01:14:00,615
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What happened to you?</font></b>

845
01:14:00,866 --> 01:14:03,034
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">He just asked Fleur Delacour out.</font></b>

846
01:14:03,201 --> 01:14:05,704
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- What?
- What did she say?</font></b>

847
01:14:05,871 --> 01:14:07,247
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No, of course.</font></b>

848
01:14:08,790 --> 01:14:12,127
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- She said yes?
- Don't be silly.</font></b>

849
01:14:12,544 --> 01:14:16,965
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">There she was, walking by.
You know how I like it when they walk.</font></b>

850
01:14:17,716 --> 01:14:21,344
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I couldn't help it.
It just sort of slipped out.</font></b>

851
01:14:21,511 --> 01:14:24,931
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Actually, he sort of screamed at her.
It was a bit frightening.</font></b>

852
01:14:26,141 --> 01:14:29,769
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- And what did you do then?
- What else? I ran for it.</font></b>

853
01:14:29,936 --> 01:14:33,648
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I'm not cut out for this, Harry.
I don't know what got into me.</font></b>

854
01:14:33,815 --> 01:14:35,066
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Hi, Harry.
- Hi, Harry.</font></b>

855
01:14:35,233 --> 01:14:38,320
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I always liked looking at them
from behind.</font></b>

856
01:14:39,654 --> 01:14:42,199
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">She's never gonna forgive me, ever.</font></b>

857
01:14:42,783 --> 01:14:43,825
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Hey!</font></b>

858
01:15:00,926 --> 01:15:02,636
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Bloody hell.</font></b>

859
01:15:04,846 --> 01:15:06,640
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Bloody hell.</font></b>

860
01:15:10,143 --> 01:15:11,436
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Bloody...</font></b>

861
01:15:11,603 --> 01:15:12,813
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Oh, bloody...</font></b>

862
01:15:16,525 --> 01:15:19,236
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What are those? What are those?</font></b>

863
01:15:19,402 --> 01:15:22,447
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- My dress robes.
- Well, they're all right!</font></b>

864
01:15:22,614 --> 01:15:25,534
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No lace. No dodgy little collar.</font></b>

865
01:15:25,700 --> 01:15:27,702
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Well, I expect yours are more traditional.</font></b>

866
01:15:27,869 --> 01:15:32,791
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Traditional?! They're ancient!
I look like my Great Aunt Tessie!</font></b>

867
01:15:35,210 --> 01:15:38,296
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I smell like my Great Aunt Tessie.</font></b>

868
01:15:43,051 --> 01:15:44,886
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Murder me, Harry.</font></b>

869
01:15:46,263 --> 01:15:47,848
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Leave it alone!</font></b>

870
01:15:48,807 --> 01:15:52,227
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Poor kid. I bet she's alone in her room,
crying her eyes out.</font></b>

871
01:15:52,394 --> 01:15:54,896
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Who?
- Hermione, of course.</font></b>

872
01:15:55,063 --> 01:15:58,650
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Come on, Harry, why do you think she
wouldn't tell us who she's coming with?</font></b>

873
01:15:58,817 --> 01:16:01,027
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Because we'd take the mickey out of her
if she did.</font></b>

874
01:16:01,194 --> 01:16:06,283
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Nobody asked her. Would've taken her
myself if she wasn't so bloody proud.</font></b>

875
01:16:07,242 --> 01:16:08,660
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Hello, boys.
- Hello, boys.</font></b>

876
01:16:08,827 --> 01:16:10,662
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Don't you look...</font></b>

877
01:16:11,246 --> 01:16:12,414
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...dashing.</font></b>

878
01:16:12,998 --> 01:16:16,168
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">There you are, Potter.
Are you and Miss Patil ready?</font></b>

879
01:16:16,334 --> 01:16:18,170
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Ready, professor?
- To dance.</font></b>

880
01:16:18,336 --> 01:16:21,381
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It's traditional that the three champions...
Well, in this case, four.</font></b>

881
01:16:21,548 --> 01:16:22,591
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Are the first to dance.</font></b>

882
01:16:22,924 --> 01:16:25,510
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Surely I told you that.
- No.</font></b>

883
01:16:26,136 --> 01:16:27,888
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Well, now you know.</font></b>

884
01:16:29,890 --> 01:16:33,685
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">As for you, Mr. Weasley, you may proceed
into the Great Hall with Miss Patil.</font></b>

885
01:16:33,852 --> 01:16:36,188
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Oh, there you are.
- Come on, then.</font></b>

886
01:16:36,396 --> 01:16:37,939
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Come along this way.</font></b>

887
01:16:42,778 --> 01:16:44,613
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Oh, come on.</font></b>

888
01:16:45,447 --> 01:16:47,449
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Hi.
- Now, I need you all to line up...</font></b>

889
01:16:47,616 --> 01:16:50,994
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...in the procession, please.
Oh, you are very late.</font></b>

890
01:16:53,205 --> 01:16:55,624
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">This way. This way. Come along.</font></b>

891
01:16:57,292 --> 01:16:59,544
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">She looks beautiful!</font></b>

892
01:16:59,711 --> 01:17:01,296
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Yeah, she does.</font></b>

893
01:17:48,677 --> 01:17:52,264
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Is that Hermione Granger?
With Viktor Krum?</font></b>

894
01:17:52,889 --> 01:17:55,475
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No. Absolutely not.</font></b>

895
01:18:00,188 --> 01:18:01,731
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Hi!</font></b>

896
01:18:10,490 --> 01:18:12,451
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Harry, take my waist.</font></b>

897
01:18:13,368 --> 01:18:14,786
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- What?
- Now!</font></b>

898
01:19:21,394 --> 01:19:23,146
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Are you ready?</font></b>

899
01:19:23,772 --> 01:19:25,982
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Move your body like a hairy troll</i></font></b>

900
01:19:26,817 --> 01:19:29,277
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Learning to rock and roll</i></font></b>

901
01:19:29,694 --> 01:19:32,280
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Spin around like a crazy elf</i></font></b>

902
01:19:32,781 --> 01:19:35,033
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Dancing by himself</i></font></b>

903
01:19:35,325 --> 01:19:38,662
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Boogie down like a unicorn</i></font></b>

904
01:19:38,829 --> 01:19:41,289
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>No stopping till the break of dawn</i></font></b>

905
01:19:41,456 --> 01:19:44,292
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Put your hands up in the air</i></font></b>

906
01:19:44,459 --> 01:19:47,254
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Like an ogre who just don 't care</i></font></b>

907
01:19:47,963 --> 01:19:50,632
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Can you dance like a Hippogriff?</i></font></b>

908
01:19:52,968 --> 01:19:55,137
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Ruddy pumpkinhead, isn't he?</font></b>

909
01:19:57,305 --> 01:20:00,725
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I don't think it was the books
that had him going to the library.</font></b>

910
01:20:02,644 --> 01:20:04,187
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">May I have your arm?</font></b>

911
01:20:04,354 --> 01:20:07,065
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Arm. Leg. I'm yours.</font></b>

912
01:20:33,008 --> 01:20:34,593
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Hot, isn't it?</font></b>

913
01:20:35,260 --> 01:20:38,597
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Viktor's gone to go and get drinks.
Would you care to join us?</font></b>

914
01:20:38,763 --> 01:20:42,434
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No, we'd not care to join you and Viktor.</font></b>

915
01:20:44,144 --> 01:20:46,480
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What's got your wand in a knot?</font></b>

916
01:20:46,772 --> 01:20:50,442
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">He's a Durmstrang.
You're fraternizing with the enemy.</font></b>

917
01:20:50,609 --> 01:20:54,196
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The enemy?
Who was it wanting his autograph?</font></b>

918
01:20:54,905 --> 01:20:57,365
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Besides, the whole point
of the tournament...</font></b>

919
01:20:57,532 --> 01:21:01,036
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...is international
magical cooperation...</font></b>

920
01:21:01,620 --> 01:21:03,121
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...to make friends.</font></b>

921
01:21:03,872 --> 01:21:07,042
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I think he's got a bit more
than friendship on his mind.</font></b>

922
01:21:17,010 --> 01:21:19,346
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Are you going to ask me
to dance or not?</font></b>

923
01:21:19,513 --> 01:21:20,931
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No.</font></b>

924
01:21:29,189 --> 01:21:31,608
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- He's using you.
- How dare you?!</font></b>

925
01:21:31,775 --> 01:21:35,987
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Besides, I can take care of myself.
- I doubt it. He's way too old.</font></b>

926
01:21:36,154 --> 01:21:39,825
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- What?! What? That's what you think?
- Yeah, that's what I think.</font></b>

927
01:21:39,991 --> 01:21:42,119
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You know the solution then, don't you?</font></b>

928
01:21:42,285 --> 01:21:44,287
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Go on.
- Next time there's a ball...</font></b>

929
01:21:44,454 --> 01:21:47,582
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...pluck up the courage and ask me
before somebody else does!</font></b>

930
01:21:47,749 --> 01:21:49,793
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">And not as a last resort.</font></b>

931
01:21:49,960 --> 01:21:54,172
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Well, that's... I mean,
that's just completely off the point.</font></b>

932
01:21:54,339 --> 01:21:55,674
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Harry.</font></b>

933
01:21:56,133 --> 01:21:57,425
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Where have you been?</font></b>

934
01:21:57,592 --> 01:22:00,095
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Never mind! Off to bed, both of you.</font></b>

935
01:22:02,931 --> 01:22:06,935
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- They get scary when they get older.
- Ron, you spoiled everything!</font></b>

936
01:22:07,102 --> 01:22:08,979
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What's this about?</font></b>

937
01:22:13,275 --> 01:22:16,278
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>No, don 't let</i></font></b>

938
01:22:18,071 --> 01:22:22,409
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>This magic die</i></font></b>

939
01:22:24,161 --> 01:22:26,955
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>The answer's there</i></font></b>

940
01:23:25,263 --> 01:23:27,349
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Let me see it again.</font></b>

941
01:23:28,683 --> 01:23:31,561
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Yes, the time is close now.</font></b>

942
01:23:36,274 --> 01:23:38,110
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Harry, at last!</i></font></b>

943
01:23:39,444 --> 01:23:44,783
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Step aside, Wormtail,
so I can give our guest a proper greeting.</font></b>

944
01:23:55,377 --> 01:23:56,795
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You all right, Harry?</font></b>

945
01:23:58,213 --> 01:24:00,006
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I just got in.</font></b>

946
01:24:00,590 --> 01:24:01,842
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Me.</font></b>

947
01:24:13,103 --> 01:24:16,398
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Harry, you told me
you'd figured the egg out weeks ago.</font></b>

948
01:24:16,565 --> 01:24:20,735
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- The task is two days from now.
- Really? I had no idea.</font></b>

949
01:24:22,279 --> 01:24:24,072
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I suppose Viktor's
already figured it out.</font></b>

950
01:24:24,239 --> 01:24:27,075
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Wouldn't know. We don't actually
talk about the tournament.</font></b>

951
01:24:28,285 --> 01:24:32,914
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Actually, we don't really talk at all.
Viktor's more of a physical being.</font></b>

952
01:24:36,626 --> 01:24:39,838
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I just mean he's not
particularly loquacious.</font></b>

953
01:24:40,297 --> 01:24:42,549
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Mostly, he watches me study.</font></b>

954
01:24:43,341 --> 01:24:45,427
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It's a bit annoying, actually.</font></b>

955
01:24:46,803 --> 01:24:49,514
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You are trying to figure this egg out,
aren't you?</font></b>

956
01:24:50,348 --> 01:24:51,808
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What's that supposed to mean?</font></b>

957
01:24:52,434 --> 01:24:55,437
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It just means these tasks
are designed to test you...</font></b>

958
01:24:55,604 --> 01:24:58,774
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...in the most brutal way.
They're almost cruel.</font></b>

959
01:24:59,941 --> 01:25:01,568
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">And...</font></b>

960
01:25:03,904 --> 01:25:05,781
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...I'm scared for you.</font></b>

961
01:25:06,740 --> 01:25:09,326
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You got by the dragons
mostly on nerve.</font></b>

962
01:25:09,951 --> 01:25:12,454
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I'm not sure it's going
to be enough this time.</font></b>

963
01:25:12,621 --> 01:25:14,289
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Hey, Potter!</font></b>

964
01:25:20,045 --> 01:25:21,546
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Potter!
- Cedric.</font></b>

965
01:25:24,257 --> 01:25:25,926
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">How...? How are you?</font></b>

966
01:25:26,968 --> 01:25:28,386
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Spectacular.</font></b>

967
01:25:29,930 --> 01:25:33,767
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I realize I never really thanked you properly
for tipping me off about those dragons.</font></b>

968
01:25:33,934 --> 01:25:36,228
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Forget it. I'm sure you
would've done the same for me.</font></b>

969
01:25:36,561 --> 01:25:38,146
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Exactly.</font></b>

970
01:25:39,231 --> 01:25:41,733
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You know the Prefects' bathroom
on the fifth floor?</font></b>

971
01:25:45,654 --> 01:25:48,240
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It's not a bad place for a bath.</font></b>

972
01:25:50,617 --> 01:25:52,494
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Just take your egg...</font></b>

973
01:25:53,245 --> 01:25:55,997
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...and mull things over
in the hot water.</font></b>

974
01:26:31,199 --> 01:26:33,368
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I must be out of my mind.</font></b>

975
01:26:43,545 --> 01:26:45,714
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I'm definitely out of my mind.</font></b>

976
01:26:48,383 --> 01:26:51,678
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I'd try putting it in the water
if I were you.</font></b>

977
01:26:51,845 --> 01:26:53,722
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Myrtle!</font></b>

978
01:26:53,889 --> 01:26:55,640
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Hello, Harry.</font></b>

979
01:26:56,433 --> 01:26:59,644
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Long time no see.</font></b>

980
01:27:03,899 --> 01:27:07,569
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I was circling a blocked drain
the other day...</font></b>

981
01:27:07,736 --> 01:27:11,198
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...and could swear I saw a bit
of Polyjuice Potion.</font></b>

982
01:27:11,364 --> 01:27:13,700
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Not being a bad boy again,
are you, Harry?</font></b>

983
01:27:13,867 --> 01:27:15,619
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Polyjuice Potion?</font></b>

984
01:27:16,411 --> 01:27:20,415
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Kicked the habit. Myrtle, did you say,
"Try putting it in the water"?</font></b>

985
01:27:27,255 --> 01:27:28,924
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">That's what he did.</font></b>

986
01:27:29,758 --> 01:27:31,426
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The other boy...</font></b>

987
01:27:32,844 --> 01:27:34,930
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...the handsome one...</font></b>

988
01:27:36,223 --> 01:27:37,557
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...Cedric.</font></b>

989
01:27:40,852 --> 01:27:43,522
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Well, go on. Open it.</font></b>

990
01:27:51,613 --> 01:27:56,618
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Come seek us
Where our voices sound</i></font></b>

991
01:27:56,785 --> 01:28:01,456
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>We cannot sing
Above the ground</i></font></b>

992
01:28:01,623 --> 01:28:05,961
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>An hour long you'll have to look</i></font></b>

993
01:28:06,753 --> 01:28:11,424
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>To recover what we took</i></font></b>

994
01:28:19,599 --> 01:28:21,101
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Myrtle...</font></b>

995
01:28:22,477 --> 01:28:25,939
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...there aren't merpeople
in the Black Lake, are there?</font></b>

996
01:28:26,815 --> 01:28:28,483
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Very good.</font></b>

997
01:28:29,359 --> 01:28:33,738
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It took Cedric ages to riddle it out.</font></b>

998
01:28:34,239 --> 01:28:37,993
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Almost all the bubbles were gone.</font></b>

999
01:28:55,677 --> 01:28:57,637
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Harry, tell me again.</font></b>

1000
01:28:59,347 --> 01:29:02,184
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">"Come seek us
where our voices sound."</font></b>

1001
01:29:02,350 --> 01:29:04,895
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The Black Lake, that's obvious.</font></b>

1002
01:29:05,854 --> 01:29:08,398
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">"An hour long you'll have to look."</font></b>

1003
01:29:08,565 --> 01:29:12,027
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Again, obvious. Though, admittedly,
potentially problematic.</font></b>

1004
01:29:13,403 --> 01:29:15,280
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">"Potentially problematic"?</font></b>

1005
01:29:15,447 --> 01:29:18,700
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">When's the last time you held your breath
underwater for an hour, Hermione?</font></b>

1006
01:29:19,242 --> 01:29:23,580
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Look, Harry, we can do this.
The three of us can figure it out.</font></b>

1007
01:29:23,747 --> 01:29:26,249
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Hate to break up the skull session.</font></b>

1008
01:29:26,416 --> 01:29:28,418
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Professor McGonagall
wants you in her office.</font></b>

1009
01:29:28,668 --> 01:29:31,046
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Not you, Potter,
just Weasley and Granger.</font></b>

1010
01:29:31,213 --> 01:29:33,882
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">But, sir, the second task
is only hours away, and...</font></b>

1011
01:29:34,049 --> 01:29:36,676
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Exactly. Presumably Potter
is well prepared by now...</font></b>

1012
01:29:36,843 --> 01:29:38,720
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...and could do with
a good night's sleep.</font></b>

1013
01:29:38,887 --> 01:29:41,389
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Go. Now!</font></b>

1014
01:29:51,358 --> 01:29:53,151
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Longbottom!</font></b>

1015
01:29:53,318 --> 01:29:55,320
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Why don't you help Potter
put his books back.</font></b>

1016
01:30:03,995 --> 01:30:06,206
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You know,
if you're interested in plants...</font></b>

1017
01:30:06,373 --> 01:30:08,959
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>...you'd be better off with
Goshawk's Guide to Herbology.</i></font></b>

1018
01:30:09,584 --> 01:30:13,880
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Do you know there's a wizard in Nepal
who's growing gravity-resistant trees?</font></b>

1019
01:30:14,047 --> 01:30:17,801
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Neville, no offense,
but I really don't care...</font></b>

1020
01:30:18,426 --> 01:30:20,137
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...about plants.</font></b>

1021
01:30:20,470 --> 01:30:22,180
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Now, if there's...</font></b>

1022
01:30:22,347 --> 01:30:27,144
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...a Tibetan turnip that will allow me
to breathe underwater for an hour...</font></b>

1023
01:30:27,310 --> 01:30:29,813
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...then great. But otherwise...</font></b>

1024
01:30:29,980 --> 01:30:33,775
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I don't know about a turnip.
But you could always use gillyweed.</font></b>

1025
01:30:35,026 --> 01:30:37,863
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Any bets? Any bets?
- Come on, place your bets!</font></b>

1026
01:30:38,029 --> 01:30:39,489
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Step up, mates! Don't be shy.</font></b>

1027
01:30:39,656 --> 01:30:41,116
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Three lads.
- One lady.</font></b>

1028
01:30:41,283 --> 01:30:43,452
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Four go down.
- But do four come up?</font></b>

1029
01:30:43,618 --> 01:30:45,120
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Don't be so mean.</font></b>

1030
01:30:45,745 --> 01:30:47,539
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Any bets?
- Fleur's 10-1.</font></b>

1031
01:30:49,749 --> 01:30:51,751
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- You're sure about this, Neville?
- Absolutely.</font></b>

1032
01:30:51,918 --> 01:30:53,837
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- For an hour?
- Most likely.</font></b>

1033
01:30:54,004 --> 01:30:55,505
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Most likely?</font></b>

1034
01:30:55,672 --> 01:30:57,883
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Well, there is some debate
among herbologists...</font></b>

1035
01:30:58,049 --> 01:31:00,510
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...as to the effects of fresh water
versus salt water...</font></b>

1036
01:31:00,677 --> 01:31:03,346
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You're telling me this now?
You must be joking!</font></b>

1037
01:31:03,513 --> 01:31:05,474
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I just wanted to help.</font></b>

1038
01:31:05,640 --> 01:31:08,769
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Well, that makes you a right sight
better than Ron and Hermione.</font></b>

1039
01:31:08,935 --> 01:31:10,687
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Where are they anyway?</font></b>

1040
01:31:10,854 --> 01:31:13,899
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- You seem a little tense, Harry.
- Do I?</font></b>

1041
01:31:20,906 --> 01:31:23,158
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Welcome to the second task.</i></font></b>

1042
01:31:23,325 --> 01:31:26,995
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Last night, something was stolen
from each of our champions.</i></font></b>

1043
01:31:27,162 --> 01:31:28,538
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>A treasure of sorts.</i></font></b>

1044
01:31:28,705 --> 01:31:31,333
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>These four treasures,
one for each champion...</i></font></b>

1045
01:31:31,500 --> 01:31:34,211
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>... now lie on the bottom
of the Black Lake.</i></font></b>

1046
01:31:34,377 --> 01:31:35,962
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>In order to win...</i></font></b>

1047
01:31:36,129 --> 01:31:39,966
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>... each champion need only find
their treasure and return to the surface.</i></font></b>

1048
01:31:40,133 --> 01:31:42,761
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>- Simple enough, except for this:
- Put that in your mouth.</i></font></b>

1049
01:31:42,928 --> 01:31:46,556
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>They will have but one hour to do so,
and one hour only.</i></font></b>

1050
01:31:46,723 --> 01:31:50,602
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>After that, they'll be on their own.
No magic will save them.</i></font></b>

1051
01:31:51,144 --> 01:31:53,396
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>You may begin
at the sound of the cannon.</i></font></b>

1052
01:32:19,923 --> 01:32:22,884
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- What's the matter with him?
- I don't know, I can't see him.</font></b>

1053
01:32:24,219 --> 01:32:27,139
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Oh, my God.
I've killed Harry Potter.</font></b>

1054
01:32:29,057 --> 01:32:30,934
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Yeah!</font></b>

1055
01:32:32,102 --> 01:32:33,728
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What?</font></b>

1056
01:33:53,308 --> 01:33:55,477
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>The Beauxbatons champion,
Miss Delacour...</i></font></b>

1057
01:33:55,644 --> 01:33:58,146
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>... has unfortunately
been forced to retire...</i></font></b>

1058
01:33:58,814 --> 01:34:01,900
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>... so she will take no further part
in this task.</i></font></b>

1059
01:35:19,686 --> 01:35:21,480
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">But she's my friend too!</font></b>

1060
01:35:23,106 --> 01:35:24,858
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Only one!</font></b>

1061
01:36:16,201 --> 01:36:18,078
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Let's get down below.</font></b>

1062
01:36:28,130 --> 01:36:30,966
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Krum! Krum! Krum!</i></font></b>

1063
01:37:28,440 --> 01:37:30,192
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Yes!</font></b>

1064
01:37:48,293 --> 01:37:50,378
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Ascendio!</i></font></b>

1065
01:37:55,592 --> 01:37:57,302
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Harry!</font></b>

1066
01:37:59,596 --> 01:38:01,056
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">He's all right.</font></b>

1067
01:38:02,265 --> 01:38:03,725
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">He's all right. Barty!</font></b>

1068
01:38:03,892 --> 01:38:07,312
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Go get him another towel.
- I want all the judges over here now!</font></b>

1069
01:38:07,896 --> 01:38:11,358
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You saved her, even though
she wasn't yours to save.</font></b>

1070
01:38:12,067 --> 01:38:13,693
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">My little sister.</font></b>

1071
01:38:14,152 --> 01:38:15,737
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Thank you.</font></b>

1072
01:38:16,530 --> 01:38:19,241
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">And you! You helped.</font></b>

1073
01:38:19,908 --> 01:38:22,911
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Well, yeah, a bit.</font></b>

1074
01:38:30,127 --> 01:38:31,294
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Harry!
- Hermione!</font></b>

1075
01:38:31,461 --> 01:38:34,131
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Are you all right? You must be freezing.</font></b>

1076
01:38:35,382 --> 01:38:37,300
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Personally, I think
you behaved admirably.</font></b>

1077
01:38:37,467 --> 01:38:39,511
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I finished last, Hermione.</font></b>

1078
01:38:40,345 --> 01:38:44,474
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Next to last.
Fleur never got past the Grindylows.</font></b>

1079
01:38:44,641 --> 01:38:47,894
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Krum! Krum! Krum!</font></b>

1080
01:38:48,061 --> 01:38:50,939
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Come on! Come on!
- Attention!</font></b>

1081
01:38:53,275 --> 01:38:55,902
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Attention!</font></b>

1082
01:38:56,361 --> 01:39:00,240
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The winner is Mr. Diggory...</font></b>

1083
01:39:00,657 --> 01:39:04,161
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...who showed innate command
of the Bubble-Head Charm.</font></b>

1084
01:39:04,327 --> 01:39:06,997
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">However, seeing as Mr. Potter
would have finished first...</font></b>

1085
01:39:07,164 --> 01:39:12,127
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...had it not been for his determination
to rescue not only Mr. Weasley...</font></b>

1086
01:39:12,294 --> 01:39:16,590
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...but the others as well,
we've agreed to award him...</font></b>

1087
01:39:16,756 --> 01:39:18,758
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...second place...</font></b>

1088
01:39:18,925 --> 01:39:20,385
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Second place!
- Well done!</font></b>

1089
01:39:20,552 --> 01:39:23,221
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...for outstanding moral fiber!</font></b>

1090
01:39:24,473 --> 01:39:26,016
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Yes!</font></b>

1091
01:39:29,519 --> 01:39:31,313
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Right on.
- All that moral fiber, eh?</font></b>

1092
01:39:31,480 --> 01:39:33,148
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- It's great.
- Moral fiber?</font></b>

1093
01:39:33,315 --> 01:39:35,650
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Blimey. Even when you go wrong,
it turns out right.</font></b>

1094
01:39:35,817 --> 01:39:38,487
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Yeah, well done, Moral Fiber.
- Congratulations, Potter.</font></b>

1095
01:39:38,653 --> 01:39:40,322
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- A fine achievement.
- Thank you.</font></b>

1096
01:39:40,489 --> 01:39:42,032
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Well done, boy.</font></b>

1097
01:39:42,199 --> 01:39:45,452
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- See you at Hagrid's, Harry.
- I'm sorry we haven't spoken.</font></b>

1098
01:39:45,619 --> 01:39:49,623
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">After all, your story is one
I've heard so many times.</font></b>

1099
01:39:50,624 --> 01:39:54,085
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Quite remarkable, really.
Tragic, of course...</font></b>

1100
01:39:54,252 --> 01:39:56,213
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...to lose one's family.</font></b>

1101
01:39:58,256 --> 01:40:00,425
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Never whole again, are we?</font></b>

1102
01:40:02,677 --> 01:40:04,721
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Still, life goes on...</font></b>

1103
01:40:05,430 --> 01:40:07,099
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...and here we stand.</font></b>

1104
01:40:10,018 --> 01:40:12,687
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I'm sure your parents would be
very proud of you today, Potter.</font></b>

1105
01:40:12,854 --> 01:40:14,356
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Bartemius!</font></b>

1106
01:40:14,523 --> 01:40:18,652
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Not trying to lure Potter into one of the
Ministry's summer internships, are we?</font></b>

1107
01:40:18,819 --> 01:40:22,239
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The last boy who went into the
Department of Mysteries never came out!</font></b>

1108
01:40:34,501 --> 01:40:36,378
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">And they say I'm mad.</font></b>

1109
01:40:45,679 --> 01:40:49,391
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Now, I remember...
I remember when I first met you all.</font></b>

1110
01:40:49,558 --> 01:40:52,561
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Biggest bunch of misfits
I ever set eyes on.</font></b>

1111
01:40:53,103 --> 01:40:55,689
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Suppose you remind me
of meself a little.</font></b>

1112
01:40:55,856 --> 01:40:59,901
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- And here we all are, four years later.
- We're still a bunch of misfits.</font></b>

1113
01:41:00,068 --> 01:41:03,405
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Well, maybe,
but we've all got each other.</font></b>

1114
01:41:03,572 --> 01:41:05,115
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">And Harry, of course.</font></b>

1115
01:41:05,282 --> 01:41:10,662
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Soon to be the youngest
Triwizard champion there's ever been!</font></b>

1116
01:41:10,871 --> 01:41:12,914
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Hooray!</font></b>

1117
01:41:14,332 --> 01:41:16,835
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Hogwarts, Hogwarts
Hoggy Warty Hogwarts</i></font></b>

1118
01:41:17,002 --> 01:41:19,629
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Teach us something, please</i></font></b>

1119
01:41:29,598 --> 01:41:31,099
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Mr. Crouch?</font></b>

1120
01:41:38,190 --> 01:41:41,777
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">A man has died here, Fudge. And he
won't be the last. You must take action.</font></b>

1121
01:41:41,943 --> 01:41:43,528
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I will not.</font></b>

1122
01:41:43,695 --> 01:41:47,783
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">In times like these, the wizard world looks
to its leaders for strength, Dumbledore!</font></b>

1123
01:41:47,949 --> 01:41:49,326
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Then for once show them some!</font></b>

1124
01:41:49,493 --> 01:41:53,538
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The Triwizard Tournament will not be
canceled. I will not be seen as a coward!</font></b>

1125
01:41:53,705 --> 01:41:56,917
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">A true leader does what is right,
no matter what others think.</font></b>

1126
01:41:57,083 --> 01:41:59,878
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- What did you say to me?
- Excuse me, gentlemen.</font></b>

1127
01:42:00,045 --> 01:42:03,715
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It may interest you to know
this conversation is no longer private.</font></b>

1128
01:42:08,053 --> 01:42:09,638
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Oh, Harry!</font></b>

1129
01:42:09,805 --> 01:42:12,099
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Harry, how good to see you again.</font></b>

1130
01:42:12,933 --> 01:42:14,434
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I can come back later, professor.</font></b>

1131
01:42:14,601 --> 01:42:17,979
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Not necessary, Harry. The minister and I
are done. I'll be back in a moment.</font></b>

1132
01:42:18,146 --> 01:42:20,690
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Minister, after you.</font></b>

1133
01:42:21,233 --> 01:42:23,235
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">There you are. Your hat.</font></b>

1134
01:42:23,401 --> 01:42:27,072
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Oh, Harry, do feel free to indulge in
a little Licorice Snap in my absence.</font></b>

1135
01:42:27,239 --> 01:42:30,408
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">But I have to warn you,
they're a wee bit sharp.</font></b>

1136
01:44:01,917 --> 01:44:03,502
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Professor?</font></b>

1137
01:44:03,668 --> 01:44:06,213
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Professor.
- Yeah.</font></b>

1138
01:44:17,099 --> 01:44:20,894
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Igor Karkaroff, you have been brought
from Azkaban at your own request...</font></b>

1139
01:44:21,061 --> 01:44:22,979
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...to present evidence to this council.</font></b>

1140
01:44:23,146 --> 01:44:25,857
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Should your testimony
prove consequential...</font></b>

1141
01:44:26,024 --> 01:44:30,112
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...council may be prepared
to order your immediate release.</font></b>

1142
01:44:30,278 --> 01:44:34,866
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Until such time, you remain in the eyes
of the Ministry a convicted Death Eater.</font></b>

1143
01:44:35,033 --> 01:44:36,660
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Do you accept these terms?</font></b>

1144
01:44:37,285 --> 01:44:39,955
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- I do, sir.
- And what do you wish to present?</font></b>

1145
01:44:40,330 --> 01:44:42,791
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I have names, sir.</font></b>

1146
01:44:43,333 --> 01:44:46,962
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">There was Rosier, Evan Rosier.</font></b>

1147
01:44:49,631 --> 01:44:52,134
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Rosier is dead.
- He took a piece of me with him...</font></b>

1148
01:44:52,300 --> 01:44:54,428
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...though, didn't he?
- I didn't know.</font></b>

1149
01:44:54,636 --> 01:44:57,264
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Lf that is all the witness has to offer...
- No, no, no.</font></b>

1150
01:44:57,431 --> 01:45:00,725
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">There was Rookwood! He was a spy.</font></b>

1151
01:45:00,892 --> 01:45:03,270
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Augustus Rookwood?
Of the Department of Mysteries?</font></b>

1152
01:45:03,437 --> 01:45:04,604
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Yeah, the same.</font></b>

1153
01:45:04,771 --> 01:45:08,483
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">He passed information to You-Know-Who
from inside the Ministry itself.</font></b>

1154
01:45:09,693 --> 01:45:12,988
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Very well. Council will deliberate.</font></b>

1155
01:45:13,155 --> 01:45:15,115
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">In the meantime,
you will return to Azkaban.</font></b>

1156
01:45:15,282 --> 01:45:19,995
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No! Wait, please! Please, I have more!
What about Snape? Severus Snape?</font></b>

1157
01:45:20,162 --> 01:45:23,165
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">As the council is aware,
I've given evidence on this matter.</font></b>

1158
01:45:23,331 --> 01:45:27,294
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Severus Snape was indeed a Death Eater
and, prior to Lord Voldemort's downfall...</font></b>

1159
01:45:27,461 --> 01:45:30,464
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...turned spy for us at great personal risk.
- It's a lie!</font></b>

1160
01:45:30,630 --> 01:45:34,092
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Today he's no more a Death Eater than I.
- Snape remains faithful to the Dark Lord!</font></b>

1161
01:45:34,259 --> 01:45:36,511
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Silence!</font></b>

1162
01:45:37,137 --> 01:45:40,557
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Unless the witness possesses
any genuine name of consequence...</font></b>

1163
01:45:40,724 --> 01:45:42,851
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...this session is now concluded.</font></b>

1164
01:45:43,018 --> 01:45:45,061
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Oh, no, no, no.</font></b>

1165
01:45:46,021 --> 01:45:47,522
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I've heard about one more.</font></b>

1166
01:45:47,689 --> 01:45:50,233
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- What's that?
- The name.</font></b>

1167
01:45:50,400 --> 01:45:51,860
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Yes?
- I know for a fact...</font></b>

1168
01:45:52,027 --> 01:45:54,070
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...this person took part
in the capture...</font></b>

1169
01:45:54,237 --> 01:45:56,406
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...and, by means
of the Cruciatus Curse...</font></b>

1170
01:45:56,573 --> 01:46:00,076
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...torture of the Auror Frank Longbottom
and his wife!</font></b>

1171
01:46:00,243 --> 01:46:02,579
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The name.
Give me the wretched name!</font></b>

1172
01:46:02,746 --> 01:46:05,290
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Barty Crouch...</font></b>

1173
01:46:08,001 --> 01:46:09,044
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...Junior.</font></b>

1174
01:46:18,512 --> 01:46:20,222
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Hold him down!</font></b>

1175
01:46:23,850 --> 01:46:27,479
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Get your filthy hands off me,
you pathetic little men!</font></b>

1176
01:46:29,189 --> 01:46:30,774
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Hello, Father.</font></b>

1177
01:46:32,192 --> 01:46:34,236
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You are no son of mine.</font></b>

1178
01:46:45,580 --> 01:46:50,043
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Curiosity is not a sin, Harry.
But you should exercise caution.</font></b>

1179
01:46:51,419 --> 01:46:52,796
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It's a Pensieve.</font></b>

1180
01:46:52,963 --> 01:46:57,634
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Very useful if, like me,
you find your mind a wee bit stretched.</font></b>

1181
01:46:57,801 --> 01:47:01,346
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It allows me to see once more
things I've already seen.</font></b>

1182
01:47:01,805 --> 01:47:04,766
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You see, Harry, I have searched
and searched for something...</font></b>

1183
01:47:04,933 --> 01:47:06,518
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...some small detail...</font></b>

1184
01:47:07,936 --> 01:47:10,063
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...something I might have overlooked...</font></b>

1185
01:47:10,230 --> 01:47:14,443
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...something that would explain why
these terrible things have happened.</font></b>

1186
01:47:15,235 --> 01:47:19,114
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Every time I get close to an answer,
it slips away.</font></b>

1187
01:47:20,157 --> 01:47:21,783
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It's maddening.</font></b>

1188
01:47:24,161 --> 01:47:25,871
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Sir? Mr. Crouch's son.</font></b>

1189
01:47:26,621 --> 01:47:28,707
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What exactly happened to him?</font></b>

1190
01:47:28,874 --> 01:47:33,670
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">He was sent to Azkaban.
Destroyed Barty to do it.</font></b>

1191
01:47:34,337 --> 01:47:37,966
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">But he had no choice.
The evidence was overwhelming.</font></b>

1192
01:47:39,426 --> 01:47:42,387
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Why do you ask?
- It's just that I...</font></b>

1193
01:47:43,138 --> 01:47:45,265
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I had a dream about him.</font></b>

1194
01:47:47,517 --> 01:47:50,312
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It was in the summer, before school.</font></b>

1195
01:47:52,481 --> 01:47:55,484
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>In the dream, I was in a house.</i></font></b>

1196
01:47:55,650 --> 01:48:00,447
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>And Voldemort was there,
only he wasn 't quite human.</i></font></b>

1197
01:48:00,614 --> 01:48:04,242
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>And Wormtail was there too.
And Mr. Crouch 's son.</i></font></b>

1198
01:48:04,618 --> 01:48:07,454
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>- Have there been others like this dream?
- Yes.</i></font></b>

1199
01:48:08,288 --> 01:48:09,915
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Always the same one.</font></b>

1200
01:48:12,959 --> 01:48:15,295
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Sir, these dreams...</font></b>

1201
01:48:15,462 --> 01:48:20,675
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...what I see, you don't think
it's actually happening, do you?</font></b>

1202
01:48:22,260 --> 01:48:25,263
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I think it's unwise for you
to linger over these dreams, Harry.</font></b>

1203
01:48:25,764 --> 01:48:27,724
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I think it's best if you simply...</font></b>

1204
01:48:33,355 --> 01:48:35,148
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...cast them away.</font></b>

1205
01:48:44,407 --> 01:48:48,370
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It's a sign, Severus.
You know what it means as well as I.</font></b>

1206
01:48:57,087 --> 01:48:58,296
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Potter!</font></b>

1207
01:48:58,463 --> 01:49:01,007
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What's your hurry?</font></b>

1208
01:49:06,096 --> 01:49:09,891
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Congratulations, your performance
in the Black Lake was inspiring.</font></b>

1209
01:49:10,058 --> 01:49:12,310
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Gillyweed, am I correct?</font></b>

1210
01:49:13,061 --> 01:49:14,604
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Yes, sir.</font></b>

1211
01:49:15,564 --> 01:49:16,940
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Ingenious.</font></b>

1212
01:49:18,775 --> 01:49:22,737
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">A rather rare herb, gillyweed.</font></b>

1213
01:49:23,572 --> 01:49:27,075
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Not something found
in your everyday garden.</font></b>

1214
01:49:28,743 --> 01:49:30,704
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Nor is this.</font></b>

1215
01:49:34,916 --> 01:49:36,585
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Know what it is?</font></b>

1216
01:49:37,878 --> 01:49:39,296
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Bubble juice, sir?</font></b>

1217
01:49:39,880 --> 01:49:41,757
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Veritaserum.</font></b>

1218
01:49:42,507 --> 01:49:46,219
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Three drops of this and You-Know-Who
himself would spill his darkest secrets.</font></b>

1219
01:49:46,386 --> 01:49:51,558
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The use of it on a student is,
regrettably, forbidden. However...</font></b>

1220
01:49:52,225 --> 01:49:55,270
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...should you ever steal
from my personal stores again...</font></b>

1221
01:49:55,437 --> 01:50:00,275
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...my hand might just slip over
your morning pumpkin juice.</font></b>

1222
01:50:00,442 --> 01:50:04,863
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- I haven't stolen anything.
- Don't lie to me.</font></b>

1223
01:50:05,989 --> 01:50:11,703
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Gillyweed may be innocuous,
but boomslang skin, lacewing flies?</font></b>

1224
01:50:12,412 --> 01:50:15,749
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You and your little friends are brewing
Polyjuice Potion, and believe me...</font></b>

1225
01:50:15,916 --> 01:50:18,126
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...I'm going to find out why!</font></b>

1226
01:50:44,945 --> 01:50:46,530
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Yeah!
- Yeah!</font></b>

1227
01:51:05,715 --> 01:51:07,259
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Sonorus!</i></font></b>

1228
01:51:11,513 --> 01:51:16,852
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Earlier today, Professor Moody placed
the Triwizard Cup deep within the maze.</font></b>

1229
01:51:17,018 --> 01:51:21,982
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Only he knows its exact position.
Now, as Mr. Diggory...</font></b>

1230
01:51:24,067 --> 01:51:25,861
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...and Mr. Potter...</font></b>

1231
01:51:27,737 --> 01:51:29,489
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...are tied for first position...</font></b>

1232
01:51:29,656 --> 01:51:33,785
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...they will be the first to enter the maze,
followed by Mr. Krum...</font></b>

1233
01:51:35,036 --> 01:51:38,498
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...and Miss Delacour.
- Come on! Krum! Krum! Krum!</font></b>

1234
01:51:39,416 --> 01:51:42,461
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The first person to touch the cup
will be the winner!</font></b>

1235
01:51:46,798 --> 01:51:49,551
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I've instructed the staff
to patrol the perimeter.</font></b>

1236
01:51:49,718 --> 01:51:52,637
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Should, at any point, a contestant wish
to withdraw from the task...</font></b>

1237
01:51:52,804 --> 01:51:57,309
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...he or she need only send up
red sparks with their wands.</font></b>

1238
01:51:57,642 --> 01:52:01,563
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Contestants! Gather around. Quickly!</font></b>

1239
01:52:04,691 --> 01:52:09,029
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">In the maze, you'll find no dragons
or creatures of the deep.</font></b>

1240
01:52:09,196 --> 01:52:12,574
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Instead, you'll face something
even more challenging.</font></b>

1241
01:52:12,741 --> 01:52:15,744
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You see, people change in the maze.</font></b>

1242
01:52:15,911 --> 01:52:17,621
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Oh, find the cup if you can.</font></b>

1243
01:52:17,788 --> 01:52:22,584
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">But be very wary, you could just
lose yourselves along the way.</font></b>

1244
01:52:24,044 --> 01:52:27,047
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Champions, prepare yourselves!</font></b>

1245
01:52:36,098 --> 01:52:37,557
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Good luck.</font></b>

1246
01:52:37,933 --> 01:52:39,893
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- My boy.
- See you later, Dad.</font></b>

1247
01:52:42,270 --> 01:52:44,856
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">On the count of three. One...</font></b>

1248
01:56:12,647 --> 01:56:13,857
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Fleur?</font></b>

1249
01:56:15,525 --> 01:56:16,985
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Fleur.</font></b>

1250
01:56:20,530 --> 01:56:22,365
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Periculum!</i></font></b>

1251
01:57:01,029 --> 01:57:02,531
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Get down!</font></b>

1252
01:57:03,073 --> 01:57:04,825
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Get down!</font></b>

1253
01:57:05,450 --> 01:57:06,701
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Expelliarmus!</i></font></b>

1254
01:57:16,294 --> 01:57:19,506
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No, don't! Stop!
He's bewitched, Cedric!</font></b>

1255
01:57:19,673 --> 01:57:21,716
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Get off me!
- He's bewitched!</font></b>

1256
01:57:33,395 --> 01:57:35,063
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Yes.</font></b>

1257
01:57:55,917 --> 01:57:57,711
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Harry!</font></b>

1258
01:58:00,046 --> 01:58:01,673
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Harry!</font></b>

1259
01:58:04,050 --> 01:58:05,469
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Harry!</font></b>

1260
01:58:07,929 --> 01:58:09,514
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Harry!</font></b>

1261
01:58:11,516 --> 01:58:13,268
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Reducto!</i></font></b>

1262
01:58:30,076 --> 01:58:32,579
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Thanks.
- No problem.</font></b>

1263
01:58:32,954 --> 01:58:37,667
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You know, for a moment there,
I thought you were gonna let it get me.</font></b>

1264
01:58:37,834 --> 01:58:39,586
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">For a moment, so did I.</font></b>

1265
01:58:41,463 --> 01:58:42,631
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Some game, huh?</font></b>

1266
01:58:43,632 --> 01:58:45,050
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Some game.</font></b>

1267
01:58:50,472 --> 01:58:52,140
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Go!</font></b>

1268
01:59:02,275 --> 01:59:05,320
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Go on, take it.
You saved me, take it!</font></b>

1269
01:59:05,487 --> 01:59:07,489
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Together. One, two...
- Two...</font></b>

1270
01:59:07,656 --> 01:59:08,865
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...three!
...three!</font></b>

1271
01:59:21,378 --> 01:59:24,256
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- You okay?
- Yeah. You?</font></b>

1272
01:59:31,346 --> 01:59:32,681
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Where are we?</font></b>

1273
01:59:38,353 --> 01:59:40,021
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I've been here before.</font></b>

1274
01:59:43,650 --> 01:59:45,235
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It's a Portkey.</font></b>

1275
01:59:47,070 --> 01:59:51,283
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Harry, the cup is a Portkey.
- I've been here before, in a dream.</font></b>

1276
01:59:53,368 --> 01:59:56,746
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Cedric! We have to get back
to the cup. Now!</font></b>

1277
01:59:56,913 --> 01:59:58,874
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What are you talking about?</font></b>

1278
02:00:04,129 --> 02:00:07,048
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Harry! What is it?
- Get back to the cup!</font></b>

1279
02:00:14,681 --> 02:00:17,017
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Who are you? What do you want?
- Kill the spare.</font></b>

1280
02:00:17,184 --> 02:00:19,936
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>- Avada Kedavra!
- No! Cedric!</i></font></b>

1281
02:00:31,239 --> 02:00:33,116
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Do it! Now!</font></b>

1282
02:00:45,087 --> 02:00:47,589
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Bone of the father...</font></b>

1283
02:00:47,756 --> 02:00:50,675
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...unwillingly given.</font></b>

1284
02:00:57,516 --> 02:01:00,560
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Flesh of the servant...</font></b>

1285
02:01:02,604 --> 02:01:05,774
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...willingly sacrificed.</font></b>

1286
02:01:09,861 --> 02:01:13,615
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">And blood of the enemy...</font></b>

1287
02:01:19,412 --> 02:01:21,915
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...forcibly taken.</font></b>

1288
02:01:27,963 --> 02:01:30,924
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The Dark Lord shall rise...</font></b>

1289
02:01:31,675 --> 02:01:33,635
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...again.</font></b>

1290
02:02:37,032 --> 02:02:40,410
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">My wand, Wormtail.</font></b>

1291
02:02:49,961 --> 02:02:51,922
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Hold out your arm.</font></b>

1292
02:02:52,089 --> 02:02:53,715
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Master.</font></b>

1293
02:02:53,882 --> 02:02:56,510
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Thank you, master.</font></b>

1294
02:02:56,676 --> 02:02:58,136
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The other arm, Wormtail.</font></b>

1295
02:03:38,760 --> 02:03:40,679
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Welcome, my friends.</font></b>

1296
02:03:42,097 --> 02:03:44,850
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Thirteen years it's been, and yet...</font></b>

1297
02:03:45,475 --> 02:03:50,981
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...here you stand before me
as though it were only yesterday.</font></b>

1298
02:03:51,940 --> 02:03:54,860
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I confess myself...</font></b>

1299
02:03:55,318 --> 02:03:56,903
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...disappointed.</font></b>

1300
02:03:57,571 --> 02:03:59,656
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Not one of you tried to find me.</font></b>

1301
02:03:59,823 --> 02:04:03,201
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Crabbe! Macnair!</font></b>

1302
02:04:04,119 --> 02:04:05,454
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Goyle!</font></b>

1303
02:04:07,956 --> 02:04:09,583
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Not even you...</font></b>

1304
02:04:13,462 --> 02:04:15,380
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...Lucius.</font></b>

1305
02:04:17,215 --> 02:04:22,053
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">My Lord, had I detected any sign,
a whisper of your whereabouts...</font></b>

1306
02:04:22,220 --> 02:04:25,223
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">There were signs, my slippery friend.
And more than whispers.</font></b>

1307
02:04:25,390 --> 02:04:30,562
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I assure you, my Lord,
I have never renounced the old ways.</font></b>

1308
02:04:32,272 --> 02:04:37,903
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The face I have been obliged to present
each day since your absence...</font></b>

1309
02:04:39,905 --> 02:04:42,532
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...that is my true mask.</font></b>

1310
02:04:42,908 --> 02:04:44,493
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I returned.</font></b>

1311
02:04:46,953 --> 02:04:50,832
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Out of fear, not loyalty.</font></b>

1312
02:04:52,000 --> 02:04:57,756
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Still, you have proved yourself useful
these past few months, Wormtail.</font></b>

1313
02:05:02,969 --> 02:05:05,305
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Thank you, master.</font></b>

1314
02:05:05,889 --> 02:05:07,641
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Thank you.</font></b>

1315
02:05:10,727 --> 02:05:13,105
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Such a handsome boy.
- Don't touch him!</font></b>

1316
02:05:14,564 --> 02:05:16,066
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Harry.</font></b>

1317
02:05:16,233 --> 02:05:19,027
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I'd almost forgotten you were here.</font></b>

1318
02:05:19,194 --> 02:05:23,615
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Standing on the bones
of my father. Yeah.</font></b>

1319
02:05:23,782 --> 02:05:25,158
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I'd introduce you...</font></b>

1320
02:05:25,325 --> 02:05:29,621
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...but word has it you're almost
as famous as me these days.</font></b>

1321
02:05:32,290 --> 02:05:34,960
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The boy who lived.</font></b>

1322
02:05:35,127 --> 02:05:38,046
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">How lies have fed your legend, Harry.</font></b>

1323
02:05:38,213 --> 02:05:42,217
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Shall I reveal what really happened
that night 13 years ago?</font></b>

1324
02:05:42,384 --> 02:05:47,097
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Shall I divulge how
I truly lost my powers?</font></b>

1325
02:05:47,264 --> 02:05:48,765
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Yes, shall I?</font></b>

1326
02:05:49,224 --> 02:05:50,559
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It was love.</font></b>

1327
02:05:50,725 --> 02:05:55,230
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You see, when dear, sweet Lily Potter
gave her life for her only son...</font></b>

1328
02:05:55,397 --> 02:05:57,983
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...she provided the ultimate protection.</font></b>

1329
02:05:58,400 --> 02:06:00,193
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I could not touch him.</font></b>

1330
02:06:01,403 --> 02:06:03,572
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It was old magic.</font></b>

1331
02:06:03,738 --> 02:06:05,991
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Something I should have foreseen.</font></b>

1332
02:06:06,158 --> 02:06:07,951
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">But no matter, no matter.</font></b>

1333
02:06:08,118 --> 02:06:10,328
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Things have changed.</font></b>

1334
02:06:11,079 --> 02:06:14,583
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I can touch you...</font></b>

1335
02:06:15,208 --> 02:06:16,918
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...now.</font></b>

1336
02:06:25,093 --> 02:06:26,428
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Yeah.</font></b>

1337
02:06:32,768 --> 02:06:36,438
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Astonishing what a few drops
of your blood will do, eh, Harry?</font></b>

1338
02:06:37,647 --> 02:06:39,316
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Pick up your wand, Potter.</font></b>

1339
02:06:40,942 --> 02:06:43,153
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I said, pick it up! Get up! Get up!</font></b>

1340
02:06:44,780 --> 02:06:47,073
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You've been taught how to duel,
I presume, yes?</font></b>

1341
02:06:47,240 --> 02:06:49,659
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">First, we bow to each other.</font></b>

1342
02:06:49,826 --> 02:06:52,245
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Come on, now, Harry.
The niceties must be observed.</font></b>

1343
02:06:52,412 --> 02:06:55,624
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Dumbledore wouldn't want you
to forget your manners, would he?</font></b>

1344
02:06:55,791 --> 02:06:57,125
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I said, bow.</font></b>

1345
02:06:58,960 --> 02:07:03,298
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- That's better. And now...
- No.</font></b>

1346
02:07:03,715 --> 02:07:05,592
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Crucio!</i></font></b>

1347
02:07:08,053 --> 02:07:09,805
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Crucio!</i></font></b>

1348
02:07:10,847 --> 02:07:12,808
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Attaboy, Harry.</font></b>

1349
02:07:12,974 --> 02:07:15,102
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Your parents would be proud.</font></b>

1350
02:07:15,393 --> 02:07:18,814
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Especially your filthy Muggle mother.</font></b>

1351
02:07:18,980 --> 02:07:20,565
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Expelliar...</i></font></b>

1352
02:07:23,568 --> 02:07:25,987
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I'm going to kill you, Harry Potter.</font></b>

1353
02:07:26,154 --> 02:07:28,156
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I'm going to destroy you.</font></b>

1354
02:07:30,325 --> 02:07:35,914
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">After tonight, no one will ever again
question my powers.</font></b>

1355
02:07:36,540 --> 02:07:39,126
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">After tonight, if they speak of you...</font></b>

1356
02:07:39,292 --> 02:07:41,962
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...they'll speak only of how you...</font></b>

1357
02:07:42,254 --> 02:07:44,089
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...begged for death.</font></b>

1358
02:07:44,256 --> 02:07:48,009
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">And I, being a merciful Lord...</font></b>

1359
02:07:48,552 --> 02:07:50,178
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...obliged.</font></b>

1360
02:07:50,512 --> 02:07:52,013
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Get up!</font></b>

1361
02:07:57,018 --> 02:07:58,979
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Don't you turn your back on me,
Harry Potter!</font></b>

1362
02:07:59,146 --> 02:08:01,398
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I want you to look at me
when I kill you!</font></b>

1363
02:08:01,565 --> 02:08:04,776
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I want to see the light
leave your eyes!</font></b>

1364
02:08:18,707 --> 02:08:20,459
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Have it your way.</font></b>

1365
02:08:21,501 --> 02:08:23,879
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>- Expelliarmus!
- Avada Kedavra!</i></font></b>

1366
02:08:41,396 --> 02:08:44,065
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Do nothing! He's mine to finish!</font></b>

1367
02:08:48,653 --> 02:08:50,363
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">He's mine!</font></b>

1368
02:09:23,438 --> 02:09:27,442
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Harry, when the connection is broken,
you must get to the Portkey.</font></b>

1369
02:09:27,609 --> 02:09:29,653
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">We can linger for a moment
to give you some time...</font></b>

1370
02:09:29,820 --> 02:09:31,613
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...but only a moment.
Do you understand?</font></b>

1371
02:09:32,781 --> 02:09:35,826
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Harry, take my body back, will you?</font></b>

1372
02:09:35,992 --> 02:09:38,537
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Take my body back to my father.</font></b>

1373
02:09:39,579 --> 02:09:40,914
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Let go.</font></b>

1374
02:09:41,373 --> 02:09:43,333
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Sweetheart, you're ready.</font></b>

1375
02:09:44,167 --> 02:09:46,795
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Let go! Let go!</font></b>

1376
02:09:52,551 --> 02:09:53,927
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Accio!</i></font></b>

1377
02:09:59,641 --> 02:10:01,643
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No!</font></b>

1378
02:10:14,364 --> 02:10:15,991
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">He did it!</font></b>

1379
02:10:17,200 --> 02:10:18,869
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Harry!</font></b>

1380
02:10:21,663 --> 02:10:23,165
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Harry!</font></b>

1381
02:10:24,332 --> 02:10:27,586
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No! No! No, don't!</font></b>

1382
02:10:27,878 --> 02:10:29,755
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">For God's sake, Dumbledore,
what's happened?</font></b>

1383
02:10:30,046 --> 02:10:32,632
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">He's back. He's back.</font></b>

1384
02:10:32,799 --> 02:10:34,843
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Voldemort's back.</font></b>

1385
02:10:35,010 --> 02:10:37,387
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Cedric, he asked me
to bring his body back.</font></b>

1386
02:10:37,554 --> 02:10:39,890
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I couldn't leave him, not there.</font></b>

1387
02:10:40,056 --> 02:10:42,851
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It's all right, Harry. It's all right.</font></b>

1388
02:10:43,018 --> 02:10:45,353
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">He's home. You both are.</font></b>

1389
02:10:45,520 --> 02:10:49,149
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Keep everybody in their seats.
A boy has just been killed.</font></b>

1390
02:10:52,194 --> 02:10:55,822
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The body must be moved, Dumbledore.
There are too many people.</font></b>

1391
02:10:56,156 --> 02:10:57,866
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Let me through.</font></b>

1392
02:10:58,033 --> 02:10:59,534
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Let me through!</font></b>

1393
02:11:01,453 --> 02:11:02,704
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Let me through!</font></b>

1394
02:11:02,871 --> 02:11:04,289
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">That's my son!</font></b>

1395
02:11:05,582 --> 02:11:07,042
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">That's my boy!</font></b>

1396
02:11:09,878 --> 02:11:12,589
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It's my boy!</font></b>

1397
02:11:15,383 --> 02:11:18,970
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Come on. Get up. Easy, easy!
- No.</font></b>

1398
02:11:19,137 --> 02:11:22,099
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">This is not where you want to be
right now. Come on.</font></b>

1399
02:11:22,766 --> 02:11:24,976
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No!</font></b>

1400
02:11:28,063 --> 02:11:30,440
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It's all right, I got you.</font></b>

1401
02:11:30,607 --> 02:11:33,944
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I got you. Come on. Easy, now.</font></b>

1402
02:11:37,948 --> 02:11:39,741
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No!</font></b>

1403
02:11:40,867 --> 02:11:42,744
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No!</font></b>

1404
02:12:25,120 --> 02:12:26,830
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Are you all right, Potter?</font></b>

1405
02:12:27,414 --> 02:12:29,332
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Does it hurt? That?</font></b>

1406
02:12:29,499 --> 02:12:31,293
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Not so much now.</font></b>

1407
02:12:32,252 --> 02:12:34,337
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Perhaps I'd better take a look at it.</font></b>

1408
02:12:37,466 --> 02:12:39,468
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The cup was a Portkey.</font></b>

1409
02:12:42,179 --> 02:12:44,014
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Someone had bewitched it.</font></b>

1410
02:12:44,306 --> 02:12:46,391
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What was it like?</font></b>

1411
02:12:46,725 --> 02:12:48,393
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- What was he like?
- Who?</font></b>

1412
02:12:48,560 --> 02:12:50,312
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The Dark Lord.</font></b>

1413
02:12:52,647 --> 02:12:55,734
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">What was it like
to stand in his presence?</font></b>

1414
02:12:56,985 --> 02:12:58,820
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I don't know.</font></b>

1415
02:13:01,656 --> 02:13:04,576
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It was like I'd fallen
into one of my dreams...</font></b>

1416
02:13:07,537 --> 02:13:09,539
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...into one of my nightmares.</font></b>

1417
02:13:28,266 --> 02:13:29,851
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Were there others?</font></b>

1418
02:13:30,018 --> 02:13:32,270
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">In the graveyard, were there others?</font></b>

1419
02:13:36,191 --> 02:13:37,609
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I...</font></b>

1420
02:13:38,318 --> 02:13:42,239
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I don't think I said anything
about a graveyard, professor.</font></b>

1421
02:13:49,704 --> 02:13:52,958
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">"Marvelous creatures, dragons,
aren't they?"</font></b>

1422
02:13:57,379 --> 02:14:00,424
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Did you think that miserable oaf
would've led you into the woods...</font></b>

1423
02:14:00,590 --> 02:14:02,509
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...if I hadn't suggested it?</font></b>

1424
02:14:06,054 --> 02:14:09,724
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Do you think Cedric Diggory would've
told you to open the egg underwater...</font></b>

1425
02:14:09,891 --> 02:14:12,394
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...if I hadn't told him first myself?</font></b>

1426
02:14:14,020 --> 02:14:16,690
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Did you think Neville Longbottom,
the witless wonder...</font></b>

1427
02:14:16,857 --> 02:14:20,068
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...could've provided you with gillyweed
if I hadn't given him the book...</font></b>

1428
02:14:20,235 --> 02:14:21,778
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...that led him straight to it?</font></b>

1429
02:14:30,203 --> 02:14:34,207
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">It was you from the beginning.
You put my name in the Goblet of Fire.</font></b>

1430
02:14:34,750 --> 02:14:38,420
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- You bewitched Krum, but you...
- "But... But..."</font></b>

1431
02:14:38,587 --> 02:14:40,756
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You won because I made it so, Potter.</font></b>

1432
02:14:41,381 --> 02:14:44,885
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You ended up in that graveyard tonight
because it was meant to be so.</font></b>

1433
02:14:45,051 --> 02:14:46,344
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">And now the deed is done.</font></b>

1434
02:14:48,013 --> 02:14:52,350
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The blood that runs through these veins
runs within the Dark Lord.</font></b>

1435
02:15:00,859 --> 02:15:04,362
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Imagine how he will reward me
when he learns...</font></b>

1436
02:15:05,280 --> 02:15:07,783
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...that I have once and for all...</font></b>

1437
02:15:08,408 --> 02:15:12,746
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...silenced the great Harry Potter.</font></b>

1438
02:15:12,913 --> 02:15:14,164
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Expelliarmus!</i></font></b>

1439
02:15:18,877 --> 02:15:20,128
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Severus.</font></b>

1440
02:15:22,631 --> 02:15:24,132
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">That's it, take it.</font></b>

1441
02:15:26,093 --> 02:15:29,554
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Do you know who I am?
- Albus Dumbledore.</font></b>

1442
02:15:29,721 --> 02:15:32,432
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- Are you Alastor Moody? Are you?
- No.</font></b>

1443
02:15:32,599 --> 02:15:35,685
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Is he in this room? Is he in this room?</font></b>

1444
02:15:38,730 --> 02:15:40,273
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Harry, away from there!</font></b>

1445
02:16:01,253 --> 02:16:04,589
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- You all right, Alastor?
- I'm sorry, Albus.</font></b>

1446
02:16:05,549 --> 02:16:07,634
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">That's Moody. But then who's...?</font></b>

1447
02:16:09,428 --> 02:16:10,512
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Polyjuice Potion.</font></b>

1448
02:16:10,679 --> 02:16:13,932
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Now we know who's been stealing
from your stores, Severus.</font></b>

1449
02:16:14,182 --> 02:16:16,101
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">We'll get you up in a minute.</font></b>

1450
02:16:50,552 --> 02:16:51,928
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Harry!</font></b>

1451
02:16:55,599 --> 02:16:57,809
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Barty Crouch Junior.</font></b>

1452
02:16:58,059 --> 02:17:00,979
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I'll show you mine
if you show me yours.</font></b>

1453
02:17:03,356 --> 02:17:04,566
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Your arm, Harry.</font></b>

1454
02:17:08,904 --> 02:17:11,156
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You know what this means, don't you?</font></b>

1455
02:17:12,073 --> 02:17:13,408
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">He's back.</font></b>

1456
02:17:14,576 --> 02:17:16,745
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Lord Voldemort has returned.</font></b>

1457
02:17:17,662 --> 02:17:19,998
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I'm sorry, sir. I couldn't help it.</font></b>

1458
02:17:20,207 --> 02:17:24,753
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Send an owl to Azkaban. I think
they'll find they're missing a prisoner.</font></b>

1459
02:17:25,212 --> 02:17:27,714
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- I'll be welcomed back like a hero.
- Perhaps.</font></b>

1460
02:17:28,256 --> 02:17:31,134
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Personally, I've never had much time
for heroes.</font></b>

1461
02:17:51,029 --> 02:17:53,698
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Today, we acknowledge...</font></b>

1462
02:17:54,407 --> 02:17:57,160
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...a really terrible loss.</font></b>

1463
02:17:59,287 --> 02:18:02,040
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Cedric Diggory was, as you all know...</font></b>

1464
02:18:02,207 --> 02:18:04,543
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...exceptionally hard-working...</font></b>

1465
02:18:05,502 --> 02:18:07,796
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...infinitely fair-minded...</font></b>

1466
02:18:08,380 --> 02:18:10,674
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...and, most importantly...</font></b>

1467
02:18:10,966 --> 02:18:15,554
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...a fierce, fierce friend.</font></b>

1468
02:18:16,680 --> 02:18:21,059
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Now, I think, therefore, you have
the right to know exactly how he died.</font></b>

1469
02:18:24,104 --> 02:18:25,647
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You see...</font></b>

1470
02:18:26,481 --> 02:18:28,567
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...Cedric Diggory was murdered...</font></b>

1471
02:18:29,484 --> 02:18:31,486
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...by Lord Voldemort!</font></b>

1472
02:18:33,363 --> 02:18:36,950
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">The Ministry of Magic
does not wish me to tell you this.</font></b>

1473
02:18:37,576 --> 02:18:41,288
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">But not to do so, I think,
would be an insult to his memory.</font></b>

1474
02:18:43,457 --> 02:18:45,125
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Now, the pain...</font></b>

1475
02:18:45,292 --> 02:18:48,962
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...we all feel at this dreadful loss
reminds me...</font></b>

1476
02:18:49,129 --> 02:18:50,464
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...and reminds us...</font></b>

1477
02:18:50,630 --> 02:18:54,342
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...that while we may come from different
places and speak in different tongues...</font></b>

1478
02:18:54,509 --> 02:18:57,929
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...our hearts beat as one.</font></b>

1479
02:18:58,430 --> 02:19:00,474
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">In light of recent events...</font></b>

1480
02:19:00,807 --> 02:19:05,729
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...the bonds of friendship we've made
this year will be more important than ever.</font></b>

1481
02:19:06,605 --> 02:19:11,943
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Remember that, and Cedric Diggory
will not have died in vain.</font></b>

1482
02:19:12,360 --> 02:19:14,529
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You remember that...</font></b>

1483
02:19:15,113 --> 02:19:18,158
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...and we'll celebrate a boy who was...</font></b>

1484
02:19:18,700 --> 02:19:21,161
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...kind and honest...</font></b>

1485
02:19:21,661 --> 02:19:26,249
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...and brave and true,
right to the very end.</font></b>

1486
02:19:51,483 --> 02:19:53,527
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I never liked these curtains.</font></b>

1487
02:19:54,111 --> 02:19:56,780
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Set them on fire in my fourth year.</font></b>

1488
02:19:57,114 --> 02:19:58,949
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">By accident, of course.</font></b>

1489
02:20:04,621 --> 02:20:09,000
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">I put you in terrible danger
this year, Harry. I'm sorry.</font></b>

1490
02:20:12,421 --> 02:20:14,089
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Professor...</font></b>

1491
02:20:14,297 --> 02:20:17,300
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...when I was in the graveyard,
there was a moment...</font></b>

1492
02:20:18,093 --> 02:20:22,514
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">...when Voldemort's wand and mine
sort of connected.</font></b>

1493
02:20:24,099 --> 02:20:26,435
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Priori Incantatem.</i></font></b>

1494
02:20:30,564 --> 02:20:33,275
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You saw your parents that night,
didn't you?</font></b>

1495
02:20:33,859 --> 02:20:35,694
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">They reappeared.</font></b>

1496
02:20:37,154 --> 02:20:40,949
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No spell can reawaken the dead, Harry.
I trust you know that.</font></b>

1497
02:20:43,493 --> 02:20:46,121
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Dark and difficult times lie ahead.</font></b>

1498
02:20:46,580 --> 02:20:51,418
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Soon we must all face the choice
between what is right and what is easy.</font></b>

1499
02:20:54,796 --> 02:20:56,465
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">But remember this:</font></b>

1500
02:20:56,631 --> 02:20:58,550
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You have friends here.</font></b>

1501
02:21:00,552 --> 02:21:02,304
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">You're not alone.</font></b>

1502
02:21:22,991 --> 02:21:24,743
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Hermione.</font></b>

1503
02:21:25,160 --> 02:21:27,162
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">This is for you.</font></b>

1504
02:21:27,746 --> 02:21:29,956
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Write to me. Promise.</font></b>

1505
02:21:31,041 --> 02:21:32,459
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Bye.</font></b>

1506
02:21:38,673 --> 02:21:40,634
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><i>Au revoir, Ron.</i></font></b>

1507
02:22:24,553 --> 02:22:27,097
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Do you think we'll ever just have
a quiet year at Hogwarts?</font></b>

1508
02:22:27,264 --> 02:22:28,390
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">- No.
- No.</font></b>

1509
02:22:28,557 --> 02:22:32,936
<b><font face="Comic Sans MS">No, I didn't think so. Oh, well.
What's life without a few dragons?</font></b>

1510
02:22:37,357 --> 02:22:40,193
